            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">群体类</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">group people class team human staff society generation army government family</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">关于具体名词的解读</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">总单词量：355个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">类别：38个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家通过上面的列表可以看出，具体词汇主要是指那些看得见、摸得着，或者能感受得到的具体事物。因为这个世界上的具体事物非常多，所以这一类名词就非常多，可以说占据了名词的主体，但为什么上表中仅仅列出了355个呢？像我们平时比较熟悉的elephant, desert, rice等词都不在里面，难道这些词不重要吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">不是这些词不重要，而是这些词的用法都比较简单，不存在理解和运用上的困难，只要大家背下来就可以了，所以就没有列在R词汇表中。而我们精选出来的这355个具体名词则具备以下一个或多个优良基因：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一、这个词是类别词，可以用来解释这个类别下的所有事物。马上会有详细讲解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">二、这个词除了用作名词外，还经常用作其他属性的词。如button，既可以做名词当“纽扣”讲，也可以做动词当“系上扣子”讲；key既可以做名词当“钥匙”讲，也可以做形容词当“关键的”讲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">三、这个词可以用在使用频率比较高的俚语或成语中。如cat这个词，除了当“猫”这种动物讲外，还在以下经常用到的俚语或成语中出现：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Curiosity killed the cat.好奇害死猫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Let the cat out of the bag.说漏了嘴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Its raining cats and dogs.倾盆大雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以说，在这里要特别强调一下，下面要学习的355个具体名词非常重要，但并不是说只学这355个就够了。这355个词以外常用的具体事物的名词，能记多少算多少，记不住的就用下面教给大家的技巧来解决。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这些词首先得记住！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">time plant animal insect place organization sound food meal vegetable fruit ingredient drink nutrition disease furniture jewelry cosmetics vehicle device equipment container material unit job.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">为啥呢？因为这些就是前面说过的，一个顶一百个的词。道理很容易明白，以上这些名词都是代表某一个类别的词，用这个词就可以解决它后面的这些名词。举例来说，如holiday, school, doctor, lock这四个词，分别属于时间类、地点类、职业类、装置类，所以它们就可以分别用这四个词来解释：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">holiday：a period of time when you are not at work or school</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">school：a place where children go to learn</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">doctor：a person whose job is to make ill people well again</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">lock：a device that keeps a door, gate closed that you can not open it without a key</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这就是把单词进行精确分类的好处，分得越细，越有助于我们通过它所在的类别理解这些词。更重要的是，它还能帮助我们获取前面章节所提到的一个重要的表达技巧：挑个大的。虽然上面的四个词本身就已在我们的学习范围之内，不需要再通过解释的方式进行表达，但对于其他虽然属于同类别，但却没有学过的词来说，却起着重要的作用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">比如，我们要表达“赌场”，但没学过这个词，你就可以把它用place打头进行解释：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Its a place where people win money by playing cards or something.这时候，老外就会很愉快地告诉你：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Oh, yeah, I got it. You're talking about the casino.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这样，你就很轻松地学到了一个新的单词，而且不花一分钱学费。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是一个很重要的技能，因为我们这个世界上的事物实在太多了，根本不可能都记下来，甚至其中的大部分我们连汉语的名词也不知道。所以，很多时候就需要说它的类别，然后加上相应的特征就可以把这个东西说清楚了。这个技巧就可以帮助我们节省大量背单词的时间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个技巧虽然看上去简单，在实际操作中却没那么容易。首先一点就是你要非常清楚事物所属的类别。前面给出的那些类别词有的大家比较熟悉，有的可能比较陌生。如ingredient（原料），nutrition（营养），device（装置）等。尤其是vehicle这个词，很多人会受汉语的影响，以为car就是表示“车辆”，其实它只是表示“轿车”，要想解释其他的车还得用vehicle这个真正的类别词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">报菜名有诀窍</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面就举一个例子说明掌握这些类别词对我们日常口语表达的重要作用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">比如说，我们陪外国朋友到中式餐厅吃饭，那林林总总的菜名，花样繁多，你要是想真把它们一个个准确地翻译成英语，那在吃饭之前可是需要耗费不少精力的。但有一个基本的技巧就是，你只要把你点的菜的基本原料说出来就可以了。那些老外都很熟悉的什么宫爆鸡丁啊，鱼香肉丝啊咱就不说了，举个例子，比如说酸菜鱼，你不知道酸菜怎么说，那就说成vegetable，但味道是酸的，而且有汤，所以你介绍的时候就可以说成：This dish is made of fish and vegetable.The soup is sour.再比如，韭菜炒鸡蛋，韭菜你不会说，你就可以这样介绍：This dish is made of egg and vegetable.The vegetable has long green leaves and it isspicy.聪明的老外可能就明白你说的是什么了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">关于食物的名词实在太多了，可以说一种食物就有一个名称，但我们最需要掌握的并不是各种大餐的具体名词，而是首先要知道肉（meat）怎么说，蔬菜（vegetable）怎么说，海鲜（seafood）怎么说，面包（bread）怎么说，鸡（chicken）、鸭（duck）、鱼（fish）怎么说，饮料（drink）怎么说，果汁（juice）怎么说，水果（fruit）怎么说等。掌握了这些大词，才能让我们在即使不知道某些食物的名称时也能用这些大词轻松过关。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">一个顶一万个</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这标题看上去挺吓人啊！前面刚说了get这个词可以代替一百多个动词，现在又出来了一个名词可以代替一万个？太夸张了吧？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">不夸张，真有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">前面说了，那些表示类别的词是我们首先要记住的，因为它们可能用来解释一些我们不知道的名词。但如果你连这些类别词都记不住呢？比如庄稼（crop），化妆品（cosmetics），仪器（instrument）等，因为这些词我们平时用得很少，大家还真不一定能一下说出来。还有，有些东西是没有办法自然归类的，如umbrella, wire, candle, menu等，那怎么进行解释呢？这时候就需要这个万能的名词出场了，那就是最最简单、大家最最熟悉的——thing。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个词可以用来代替所有具体名词的类别，包括上面提到的那些。无论你说一样什么东西，只要以这个为中心词，加一些辅助性的词、词组或从句进行解释就可以了。如“雨伞”不会说，你可以说the thing used when it is raining。“口红”不会说，你可以说the thing used on lips for ladies。“菜单”不会说，你可以说the thing with some dishesnames on。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">thing的作用还不仅仅是用来解释你不会的名词，有时是因为没必要一定要具体说明是个什么东西，食物啊，衣服啊都可以用这个词来代替。如下面的例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She likes sweet things.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她喜欢吃甜食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She hasn't had a thing to eat all day.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一整天了，她啥东西也没吃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Put your things on and lets go.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">穿上你的衣服跟我们走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I haven't got a thing to wear.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我都没件衣服穿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这种用法在口语中非常普遍。它给初学者带来的好处就是，当我们碰到某个名词不知道怎么说，但说话的双方都知道是什么东西的时候，就可以用thing来代替，以保证沟通的流畅性。如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Can you pass me that thing over there?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你能把那边那个东西递给我吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Turn that thing off while I'm talking to you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我跟你说话的时候把那个东西关掉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Bring your swimming things with you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">带上你游泳要用的东西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Let me clear these breakfast things.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">让我来收拾这些早餐剩下来的东西吧！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Give me that thing and I'll copy the documents for you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">把U盘给我，我来帮你复制文件。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">thing这个词不仅仅是指东西，动物甚至人都可以用thing来指代。如下面的例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You are quite a clever little thing！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你真是个聪明的小家伙！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The cat must be very hungry. Poor thing！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这只猫肯定很饿了。可怜的家伙！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有时候我们会在句子中用something来代替thing，一般是需要在后面跟一个定语从句的情况，在此不再做具体说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">thing也不仅仅指具体的物，还可以用来替代抽象的事，这是下一章节要学的内容。总之，这个词是值得大家查查词典仔细琢磨、认真掌握的黄金词汇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">抽象名词：光背下来还不行</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">话语类</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">words topic subject joke question suggestion instruction permission</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">文字类</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">document story report note text letter email list menu novel blog</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">rule：law grammar principle</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">信息类</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">information message fact detail evidence clue background data sign knowledge news update notice</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">状态类</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">state condition environment</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">situation：mess balance peace emergency chance opportunity</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">行为类</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">act practice test experiment lesson attention focus step education advertisement trick habit business exercise bath security treatment service homework</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">job：task project challenge</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">duty：responsibility fault</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">performance：concert drama opera</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">study：math art science psychology philosophy</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">arrangement：deal insurance account engagement</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">occasion：party wedding funeral picnic barbecue ceremony meeting interview</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">money：profit income salary loan cash cost credit deposit price tax bill budget</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">活动类</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">activity game discipline crime trade economy politics war trip fashion industry</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">sports：soccer football golf basketball race</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
