        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">whole rest half</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">关于构成类名词的解读</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">总单词量：65个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">类别：8个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们在描述一个事物的时候既要知道它们是什么，也要知道它们都是由什么东西构成的。这就是构成类名词的作用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">任何事物都是由一些更小的部分组成的，在英语里面，这个表示部分的词就是“part”，它可以指代所有事物的part，而不同部位的part又有自己的名称，如side（侧面），edge（边缘），base（底座），core（核心）等。在此基础上，不同事物的part又有一些具体的名称，比如人体是由不同的部位组成的，动物和人体的组成相似，但还有tail（尾巴），wing（翅膀），shell（外壳）等人类所没有的。植物也有自己独特的器官，leaf（叶子），flower（花）等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上这些部位因为比较具体，所以好理解。但因为人类是高等生物，所以除了这些具体的器官外，还有其他生物所没有的精神组成mind，而mind又分为spirit（意志），soul（灵魂），和表感情的feeling（感觉），emotion（感受）。所以，这是我们要重点掌握的内容。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有些事物是有“力量”的，这也是事物的组成部分。而人类除了“体力”之外，还延伸出智力、权力、技能等层面的“力量”，这些也是每个人的重要组成部分，是我们语言交流的重要内容之一。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了以上这些明确的part外，我们有时还需要从整体的角度来分析事情，所以还需要用到whole, rest, half这样补充性的词语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面就挑其中的两个重点词part, side进行详细说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">万物皆可分part</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">虽然有些事物的组成部分会有自己专门的名称，但几乎所有的事物都是可以用part这个词来分析表述。学会把事物分成不同的part，有助于我们更加轻松地描述和分析事物。我们看看下面的实例。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">人体组成</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">人体是由各个部位的器官所组成的。可以看到的是head, arm, leg, foot, hand, mouth, skin等，看不到的是heart, brain, liver, lung, bone等。你不可能记住身体各个器官的名字，所以，当你想描述某个特殊的器官时，只要先说一句Its part of the body.然后再说明这个器官是干什么的就可以了。同样的表达也可以用在动物和植物身上，只是植物的器官和动物的、人的器官有些不同。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">生活用品</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们吃的鸡蛋分两个部分，一个是蛋白，另一个是蛋黄，你只要说是yellow part还是white part就可以。猪肉有不同的部位，买的时候只要说是哪个part就可以。蛋糕切成不同的块，也是不同的part。一个包会分为很多层，不用考虑层怎么说，只要说是part就可以。一台电脑或机器会由很多的零部件组成，这也是part。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">区域</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">中国分华东、华南等不同的区，上海分徐汇、静安等不同的区，一个大卖场会分食品、家电等不同的区，这些都是不同的part。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">机构</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个集团公司会分不同的事业部，一个公司分不同的部门，一个学校又分不同的系，一个银行又下设一些支行，这些也都是不同的part。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">文学艺术</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小说会有不同的段落，电视剧会有不同的剧集，同一部戏里面也会有不同的角色，这些也都是part。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">当然，和其他的具体名词一样，part对我们最有价值的还是它的抽象用法。学会把一个抽象事物分成不同的part对我们的传统思维是一种挑战，但非常有价值。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">团队</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个团队里有不同的成员，这就是这个团队的part。通常我们会说member，但在某些时候用part会特别强调团队的整体意识。比如，You're part of the team.（你是团队的一分子。）就能明显地体现出这一点。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">时间</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">时间也可以分为不同的part，主要是在把时间作为一个整体看待的时候。比如，你去旅游，一共只有三天时间，那么就可以分成不同的part去做不同的事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">事件</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">前面说过，一个story会有不同side，指的是不同的说法。story也可以分成不同的part，有好的、坏的、有趣的、无聊的。如果你碰到什么事，一般只会说你表现好的part，但表现不好的你就会省略。所以，知情的人就会说：That's just part of the story.You left the stupid part.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">工作</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">每个人的工作都可以分出不同的part，不仅仅是指你做了哪些事，有时指抽象层面的东西。比如，你的工作有一定的危险性，你不能直接说My job is dangerous.这样表达会显得很严重，但又没有其他词汇可以表达，所以你就可以把它细分为一个part，把它说成：Danger is part of my job.既形象又准确。一项工作总有最难的地方，所以你可以说：That's the most difficult part of my job.有时候，别人欺负你是新人，会在公司里指使你干这干那，这时你也可以用part一词把他理直气壮地顶回去：It’s not part of my job description！每个人的工作都有个职位描述，不同的职责就是其中的一个part。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">生活</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个人在生活中需要做很多事情：交友，结婚，生孩子，做家务，运动，旅游，休闲，等等，这都是part of life。但不同的人会有不同的生活内容，比如有人喜欢喝酒，那么酒精就成了他生活的一部分，Alcohol is part of my life.对运动员来说，伤病就会是他生活的一部分，Injury is part of sportsmans life.总之，你经常做什么，什么就是part of your life。日本经常发生地震，所以对日本人来说，Earthquake is part of life in Japan.有时，我们会说：人生在世，哪有不犯错的。这句话直译不是很容易，但从part的角度出发就能迎刃而解：Making mistakes is part of life.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小试牛刀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">part的实用性还表现在它经常被用来替代其他一些词，这些词都是专门应用在某一特定语言环境下的，但都可以被part替代。以下只是列举了其中的一部分，大家可以从词典中找出它们对应的一些例句，然后用part尝试替换一下，看看是否讲得通。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">organ segment fragment slice portion wedge compartment fraction component accessory region district quarter sector division passage paragraph section episode</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">《老友记》中有802处用到part</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">《老友记》是学英语的人比较喜欢看的一部美剧。根据我们的统计，《老友记》中一共有802处用到了part，可见这个词在口语中使用的频繁程度。我把其中一些有代表性的台词整理出来，让大家进一步体会part无所不能的神奇作用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">What you guys don't understand is, for us, kissing is as important as any part of it.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你们男孩子不懂的是，对我们女孩子来说，接吻和约会的其他内容一样，都是非常重要的。（指约会）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I mean presumably, the biggest part of your job is done.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我是说，你工作中最重要的部分可能已经完成了。（指工作）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You got the clothes clean. Now thats the important part.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">衣服洗干净了，这才是最重要的。（指洗衣服）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Well, you know, part of me wants that, but it's like I'm two guys, you know?I mean, one guy's going'Shut up！This is great！But there's other guy……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你知道吗？我想这样做，但又犹豫不决，就好像两个小人，一个对我说，闭嘴！这是多好的一件事啊！但同时又有另一个小人……（指想法、念头）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Oh, and shes pregnant with my baby. I always forget that part.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">噢，对了！她怀了我的孩子，我差点把这茬给忘了！（指关系）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I know it's frightening, but, big picture. The birth part is just one day, and when it’s over, were all gonna be parents for the rest of our lives.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">（生孩子）是挺吓人的，但往远处想想。生孩子只是一天的事，但那之后，我们就是永远的父母啦！（指生孩子）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">you left out the stupid part.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你漏掉了（你表现）愚蠢的部分。（指叙述的故事）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Look, I told you I am not a part of this thing.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">听着！我告诉过你了这事没我的份儿。（指活动）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She was a big part of my life there, you know, and now I just feel kind of alone.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她是我生活中不可或缺的部分，现在我觉得有些孤单。（指生活）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You know there isn't a part of that sentence I don’t need explained.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请把你那句话的每个字都解释清楚。（指言语）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">All right, this is my favorite part of the weekend.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">好吧！这是我这个周末过得最开心的时候。（指过周末）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Phoebe：Yes. Did you settle the bill?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">菲比：你结账了吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Monica：No. I hate this part.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">莫妮卡：没呢！要是只吃饭不结账该多好。（指吃饭）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I just have to make enough money for the second part of my plan.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我得挣够钱，以便实施第二阶段的计划。（指计划）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">So I'm done my part, okay. It’s your responsibility now, okay.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">好了，我的事情已做完了，该你了！（指职责）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The good parts coming up. Keep going.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">精彩的节目马上上演了！别急。（指读书或看电视）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Is that part of your resolution, your new thing for today?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这就是你的新年心愿吗？每天做一件新的事情？（指决心）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">谁都有不为人知的一面：side</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">像万物皆有自己的part一样，任何事物也都有自己的side。有句俗话叫：千人千面。这儿的面就是指side。可惜的是，多数学生对side的认识太浅，只知其一，不知其二三四五六。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个平面有两个side，如一张纸就有一正一反两个side，而一枚硬币也有两个side。平时我们吃煎蛋的时候还会选择单面煎还是双面煎，这也是side。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">而一个立体则可能有几个不同的side，比如爬山，你可以选择从不同的side上山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">side除了指面，也指边。像一张纸或长条桌子除了正反两个面，两个长的边，也叫side。而一条路的side既可指路边，比如说Park your car at the side of a road.也可指路的两面，在中国开车要靠右边这个side行驶。我们的身体也分左右两边，三个人照相的话会有一个人在中间in the center，而另两个on each side。脸和大脑也分左右两个side。一张床两人睡，各躺一个side。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">side还可以组合成新的词，如inside, outside, upside, downside，也是指不同部位的side。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">延伸出来，side可以指任何一个事物的正反两方。比如，一个账户分贷方和借方，就是指side。一个家庭也有两个side，父亲那一边的和母亲那一边的。英语中不分堂兄妹和表兄妹，而是统称为cousin，所以你要分清是哪个side的cousin。而一场比赛由两个队伍参加，也是两个side。辩论的时候会分正方和反方。朝鲜举行了好几轮六方会谈，那就是六个side。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">对于同一件事情，不同的人会有不同的说法，这是different sides of the story。我们说兼听则明，偏信则暗，也是指要listen to both sides。任何事物都既有光明的一面（bright side），也有黑暗的一面（dark side），当然，我们一般会劝别人look on the bright side。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You're hearing one side of the story.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你听到的只是一面之词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There're two sides of this story.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这件事有两个不同的版本。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You only heard Monica's side of that.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你只是听了莫妮卡的说法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个人也会有不同的side，也就是我们经常说的人有多面性，请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She brings this greatest side out of me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她让我展示出了最好的一面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">好友或者伴侣的激励有时候能够极大地激发出人的潜能，让你焕发出无限的热情，并把你的长处发挥出来，这句话描述的就是这种情况。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He has a soft side.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他有他温柔的一面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话在汉语中也经常用到。你也可以说He does have his sweet side.下一次向你的女友夸自己的男朋友的时候，就可以用上这句话了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This is not a good side of me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这不是我好的一面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">当一件事出现争执的时候，也就产生了不同的side。这时候就会面临着选择的问题，请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Whose side are you on?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你站在哪一边？（男同胞经常会被问到这个问题，尤其是在老婆和母亲产生纠纷的时候。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Everybody chooses sides.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">任何人都会有所倾向。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Pick a side and stay there.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">选出你支持的一方，不要改来改去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
