        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">关于属性类名词的解读</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">总单词量：70个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">类别：12个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">想要了解一个事物光知道它是什么类别、由啥组成的还不够，还得知道它都有些什么特点，也就是它的属性。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">属性也要从两方面来看，一是“人”和“物”的属性，因为这两者是静态的，所以我们叫它静态属性；二是“事”的属性，因为“事”是发展变化的，有原因有结果，所以我们叫它动态属性。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">静态属性大多是看得见或感受得到的，主要是回答了下面几个问题：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">它长什么样？shape</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">它有多大？size</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">品质如何？quality</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">处在什么位置？position</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这些属性可否量化？amount</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事的属性主要是用来描述事物的发展变化，所以，除了可以借用以上物的属性外，还主要回答了以下几个问题：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">它是怎么发展的？way</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">它的目的是什么？purpose</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">发生的原因是什么？cause</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">结果如何？effect</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，事物的属性远远不止这些。所有用来描述一个事物的形容词都可以被看成事物的某一类属性，比如形容词big就是用来描述size这个属性的，heavy就是用来描述weight这个属性的。那么，形容词possible就可以说是用来描述possibility这个属性的，叫“可能性”，而important就是用来描述importance这个属性的，叫“重要性”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">但是，因为这些属性非常多，通常都是直接用形容词来表述的，所以就没在这里单独列出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们表中给出的都是“人”“事”“物”这三大类事物共同且基本的属性，已经足够用来描述这三类事物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面主要就其中最重要、最具有普遍意义的几个属性shape, size, point, line, end, amount, level, way进行讲解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">物有形人有貌：shape</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">描述一个东西，最直观的是看它是什么形状，这就是shape；要描述一个人，最直观的则是看他的长相，这就是appearance。appearance比较简单，在这里就不做重点介绍了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">先来说shape，对这个词我们掌握的难点有两个。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一是不知道如何用shape来描述事物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">比如，苹果的形状一般是圆的，这就是它的shape。除了圆形，常见的形状还有三角形、长方形等，这些会在形容词里学到。另外还有一种叫心形，也是一种shape，可以表达为in the shape of a heart。还有一种是菱形，其实就是钻石的形状，我们也可以表达为in the shape of a diamond。还有用字母形状描述的V形、O形、T形等。总之，不管是什么形，只要用in the shape of something来表达就可以了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">二是不知道生活中有很多事物可以用shape来描述。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">比如说房形、脸形、眉形、蛋糕的形状、情趣巧克力的形状等，统统可以用shape这个词来表达。除此之外，人的身体也可以用shape来描述，只不过这时表达的是你是否健康，是一种比喻。如果你身体健康，那就是in shape，不健康就是out of shape，还是很形象的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">shape还可以延伸出来表示模模糊糊看不清楚的影子，如：I can just see a dark shape.我只能看到一个黑乎乎的影子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">尺寸很重要：size</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所有的具体事物都有自己的尺寸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">房子、家具、电视</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们买的很多东西都需要关注尺寸，比如房子，就是按size卖的，买电视也要先确定是多少inch的，那也是size。家里添家具，必须先量好size，不然可能摆不进去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">衣服、鞋子、首饰</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">买衣服得看尺寸，衣服、鞋子都要按你的size买。还有买戒指，也得看好size，不然戴不上或戴不住。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">食物</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">吃的东西也要关注尺寸，如过生日买蛋糕，尺寸越大越贵。必胜客的比萨，也是按size卖的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">三围</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女孩子比较关注的胸围、腰围、臀围，都是size，当然你也可以用measurement，但size足以说明问题。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">照片、场地</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">冲洗照片要事先说好size，找个地方踢足球也要看场地的size够不够大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">文件、字体</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们办公的时候也经常会涉及size的用法，如文件的大小，太大了U盘放不下，那也是size。我们打字的时候会说用几号字，那是letter的size。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">重要性、艰巨性</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果仅仅是指实物的尺寸或大小的话，那么还体现不出这个属性词使用的广泛性。不知大家是否还记得我们在前面的章节用size分别表达过问题的严重性、任务的艰巨性以及账单？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Nobody realized the size of the problem.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She knows the size of the task.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We were shocked at the size of his debts.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">地震强度</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这就是size的延伸用法，就是说通过比喻使一些抽象事物也有它的size。我们评估地震强度的时候一般说震级magnitude，这是一个比较专业的词汇，其实你完全可以用size这个词来代替。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">市场容量、投资回报</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们写商业报告的时候经常需要讨论市场的大小，这就是市场的size, size of the market。决定一项投入之前，我们要先评估一下回报，也可以称之为size of the prize。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小试牛刀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">给大家出几个题目，看看你们是否能猜得出在下面一些表达中size的含义：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">size of happiness</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">size of government</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">size of population</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">世界是由点组成的：point</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果说一定要在所有的位置属性里面找出一个最有能耐、最具代表性的名词的话，那就一定非point莫属了。它既可以表达地点属性，也可以表达时间属性，还能延伸出来表示目标、事物的特点、发展阶段等，以它为基础生成的词汇数不胜数。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">point这个词如果直译的话就是“点”，我们汉语当中经常说的“地点”“时间点”就比较恰当地反映了这个词的基本词义，一是表示位置point of place，二是表示时间point of time。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">地点</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其实所有的空间位置，包括某个建筑、地方、地区、城市等归结到底都是一个个“点”，这是为什么我们叫它们“地点”的原因。当然，我们一般会直接称呼为place, area, city，但当我们需要特别说明是个什么样的地点时，就需要恢复它最初的样子了，如出发的地点叫departure point，会合的地点叫meeting point，检查点叫checkpoint。总之，如果不需要特别说明你讲述的地方名称是什么的时候，就可以用point来代替。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">站点</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">point用作地点并不难理解，因为我们学几何的时候都学过，点连成线，线连成面，最终才形成立体的东西，那么这个点就是最基础的了。我们生活中有很多线状的事物，如地铁，我们就叫一号线（line 1），二号线（line 2），而这些line就是由一个个的点连起来组成的，我们通常会叫station或stop，其实说白了它们就是point of the line，我们说The line are made of many stations.也可以说The line are made of many points.公交线路也一样。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">温度</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">生活中，我们经常用到“点”的词还有沸点、冰点、熔点，其实这也是英语中的点，分别是boiling point, freezing point, melting point。这些都是指某种事物发展变化的关键点。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">只要是一个持续性变化的事物，你都可以给它分出各种“点”来。打个比方，你做饭的时候就有各种点，比如“把油加热到冒烟”（Heat the oil to the point of smoke.）“翻炒至变色”（Fry it to the point of turning brown.）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">事物的发展阶段</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">由此延伸到事物发展的普遍规律，如事物的发展会有个转折点，也叫拐点（turning point）。有时候，事物的发展会有个胶着停滞不前的阶段，这就叫sticking point。如果事情发展到不可收拾的地步，就是断点（breaking point）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">任何事物的发展都有它的起点starting point和终点end point，这中间又会经历各种关键点，除前面说的turning point、sticking point和breaking point之外，还会有些闪光点high point和不那么尽如人意的点low point，或者是good point, bad point。比如一部电影或者一场比赛，总有精彩的部分，就可以叫high point，当然我们也可以叫highlight。一个人的职业生涯也有它的高潮（high point）、低谷（low point）。比如，他达到了事业的顶峰，你就可以说：He reached the high point of his career.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">重点</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个事物总有些点是非常重要的，就是我们平常所说的“重点”，我们也只要用point就可以，不需要说important point。比如说，“他开门见山，直奔重点”就可以说He comes to the point.还可以说“重点是什么什么”，如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The point is you've got to get some kind of job.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">重点是，你得找份工作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">情绪</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们经常会说“笑点”，也可以用point来表达，是指point of joke。如果说你错过了笑点（也就是相声常说的“包袱”），可以说成：You missed the point of joke.除了笑有点之外，哭也有它的点，如：她累得都快哭了。（She was tired to the point of crying.）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">特点</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">当我们描述一个人的时候，会说这个人有什么优缺点，其实就是强项strong point和弱项weak point的意思。“我上学的时候数学是我的强项”，就可以说成：Math was my strong point at school.一份报告有优点有缺点，也可以说成good points或bad points。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">卖东西我们需要有个卖点，叫selling point。当然，你可以拿来做卖点的一定是你产品的strong point或good point。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">时间点</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">和地点的表达一样，只是强调的是某一个点而无须说明什么时间或时间段，就可以用point来表达，一般是指在这个时间点有件事情发生了。如下面几个句子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He was on the point of saying something when the phone rang.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他正要说话的当口，电话响了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">At that point I had to leave.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">在那个点上，我不得不离开。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He arrived at this point.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他恰恰在那个时候赶到了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The point comes to say goodbye.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">说再见的时候到了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">人这一生就像一条生命线，会有不同的时间点。比如某个时间点要上学，某个时间点要工作，某个时间点要恋爱，某个时间点要结婚。当然，最后还会离开这个世界We are going to die at some point.用point来表达的话会更加清晰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">观点</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是point最重要的角色。这个点既不是位置上的点，也不是时间上的点，而是你观察理解事物后所总结出来的点，所以叫“观点”（point of view）。view是观察、理解的意思。当然，大多数时候，我们会直接说the point。一般会说Whats your point?你可以有自己的观点（have a point），或者是给出你的观点（give your point），你听懂了就是（get the point），当然你可以接受别人的观点（take the point），有时你还需要证明你的观点（prove the point）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">意义</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了表达观点，point还可以表示目的和意义。我们做任何事情都需要有它的point，如学习有学习的point，工作有工作的point，生孩子有生孩子的point。我们完全可以用point这个比较形象的词来代替purpose, goal, objective这些比较抽象的词。反过来说，point是这些词的祖宗，这些词都是在point的基础上生成的。在英语中，意义（meaning）和用处（function）也是从“目的”发展过来的，所以在很多场合也可以用point代替。如“我的生活失去了意义”，你可以说成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My life has lost its meaning.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">也完全可以说：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My life has lost its point.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事情要有意义我们才会去做，不然我们就会问：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Whats the point of doing something?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">世界的秩序：line</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有了点之后，紧接着要做的事情就是把它们连成线，这是line的重要性仅次于point的原因。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">line是现实中最常见的形状。不但有很多实物都是以线的形状存在的，很多抽象概念其实也是集合起来的一条线。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">可归结为一条线的东西有：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">钓鱼线　fishing line</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">晾衣绳　He hung the towels out on the line.（可代替rope）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">铁道　The train was delayed because a tree had fallen across the line.（可代替railway）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">电话线　Were thinking about getting a second line installed for the computer.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">缆绳　They dropped the sails and threw a line to a man on the dock.（可代替cable）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">皱纹　I'm getting little lines around my eyes.（可代替wrinkle）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">排队　I waited in line for over an hour to get my license.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">起跑线　starting line</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">终点线　finishing line</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球场边线　The ball went over the line.（可代替boundary）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">国界线　They fled across the line.（可代替border）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">运行路线　Light travels in a straight line.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">线条　A beautiful sports car with sleek lines.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">诗行　Read the first two lines of the poem.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">流水线　assembling line</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">通过以上例子可以看出，只要是具有线条形状的事物，不管是实的或虚的，都可以用一个简单的line来表示，它可以代替大量其他的名词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了它的具体词义外，line还引申出以下抽象词义：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">行业或家族</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">由于line是由一系列的点组成的，所有这些点具备相似的特征，所以可以用来形容某个具有统一特征的行业或公司，如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">what line of work are you in?你是做哪一行的？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">airline航空公司</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">shipping line船运公司</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">家族</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">同样的原因，line也可以用来形容某个源远流长的家族：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She comes from a long line of actors.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她出身于演员世家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">立场</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">line可以用来作为界线，所以又可以引申为观点或立场上的不同。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The governor has taken a hard line on illegal immigration.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">在非法移民这个问题上，州长采取了严厉的态度。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">What's the candidate's line on abortion?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">在堕胎这个问题上候选人持何种态度？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">秩序</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">组成line的点是一个接一个按顺序进行的，所以可以用来形容某个组织的排列次序。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Orders came down the line from the very top.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">命令从最高层逐级传达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is second in line to the chairman.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他的职位仅次于主席。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">任何事物都有终结点：end</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">end是指一条线的最后一个point，或者最后一段part。这个词大家都认识，我们经常说in the end，但很多学习者却连它的基本词义都不会用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">生活用品</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一般来说，长条状的东西都有自己的end。一条绳子就有两个end，就是我们平时说的这一头和那一头，那么水管也有两个end。抽烟的时候含在嘴里的end叫烟嘴，点上火的end叫烟头，抽完剩下的烟蒂也叫end。许多人不知道如何称呼一张桌子的四个边，如果桌子是长条状的，那么短的边叫end，长的边叫side。所以当我们说把两张桌子并在一起的时候，你要说清楚是side by side，还是end by end。同样地，一张床一般也有两个end和两个side，这就是我们将床头的小桌子叫end table的原因。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">江河道路</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">河或者长条形的湖也有两个end。游泳池一般分为浅水区和深水区，叫deep end和shallow end。公路、铁路都有它的终点end。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">队伍</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们管排队叫line，所以它也有两个end，排队时不能插队，需要wait at the end of the line。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">时间生命</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">延伸开来，时间也有它的end。时间本身没有尽头，但一个时间段或一件事则有它的end，如月末（end of the month），年末（end of the year）。我们管年终会议叫year-end meeting。一场比赛有个end，学生时代有个end，一段婚姻也有个end，职业生涯、演艺生涯都有个end，连我们的生命都有个end，那是end of the life。我们说“天下没有不散的筵席”，All good things have an end.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">故事</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个故事也有它的end，一部电影也是，我们经常在片尾看到“the end”。当然我们希望所有的故事都有一个happy end，但事情往往并非如此。有时候我们会这样安慰自己，Its not the end of the world.（这不是世界末日。）嗯，这才是对的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">感情</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">辛晓琪的成名曲《领悟》中唱道：“一段感情就此结束”，就是：That's the end of a relationship.连这么深的感情都有end。当然，我们可以对着心爱的人大喊：我要爱你到天荒地老！（I’ll love you till the end of time.）但这只是个美好的愿望而已，因为你活不过时间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">希望</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个人的希望也会有个end。当马航的飞机被宣布坠毁的时候，对遇难者家属来说，It's the end of their hope.一个人的责任也有end。当马航开了个新闻发布会宣布飞机失联之后，That's not the end of their responsibility.他们还要继续打捞失联飞机，处理赔偿事宜，等这些都处理好了，才算有一个了结。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">量化我们的世界：amount, level</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">属性词是用来说明事物都具备哪方面的特征的，但如何描述这些特征，每个事物的具体特征又是什么样的，则是另一个需要解决的问题。这个问题的解决方法之一就是把事物的特征进行量化。量化主要有三种形式：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第一种，精确。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所谓“精确量化”，就是把事物的属性以精确的数字形式进行量化。amount就是这个关键的词，而number作为数量的具体执行者，有时可以直接代替amount。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有很多表示数量的词其实都是事物某一个具体属性的量化。如长度（length），宽度（width），高度（height），距离（distance）就是某一个空间属性的amount；temperature就是热量的amount；volume就是容积的amount；而angle则是用来衡量方向的amount。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其实，如果把时间也看成事物的一种属性的话，那么年龄age也可以看成时间的量化。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第二种，分级。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有时，我们没有必要把事物的属性量化得那么精确，只要简单地分几个档次就可以，那么就可以用level来表示。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">level又可以生成更加具体的词，如degree可以指学问高低的level，所以我们有bachelor, master之分，而grade既可以指学习进度的分级，也可以指产品质量的高低。rank则是指在某一机构中的职位，如公司、军队中位置的高低。standard则是指达到要求或者能被接受的某一个具体的level。比如，你可以这样说：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The product is in grade B. Its good, but our standard is grade A.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第三种，对比。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们有时需要将事物的属性与相关数字进行对比，比如时间，以便看出效果，那么就需要用到rate这个词。如speed，就是指距离与时间对比后的rate，比率ratio则是指同一事物两个组成部分之间的rate，而比例proportion则是指某一个组成部分与整体对比后的rate。percentage是把对比的结果用100作为基数。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">通过以上分析可以看出，amount, level, rate是表示数量的三个最根本的词，需要我们牢牢把握。下面就重点说说amount和level的用法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">amount</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">amount作为数量来讲可以用来描述任何可以量化的事物，如时间、金钱等，可以用来代替我们经常使用的a little, a lot, much等，使得我们的表达更加准确和丰富。请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">金钱</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Please pay the full amount by the end of the month.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请在月底前付清全款。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">水</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Cook the vegetables in a small amount of water.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">做蔬菜要放少量的水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">酒</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I couldve married Joey with that amount of alcohol.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">喝了那么多酒，我也会娶乔伊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">车辆</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There was a fair amount of traffic on Highway 10.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">10号公路上车辆相当多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">生活用品</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I use exactly what the gel bottle says, an amount about the size of a pea.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我严格按照发胶瓶上的说明，用差不多一粒豌豆大小的量。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">时间</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It was a certain amount of time ago, I was here, you were here.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">某某时间以前，我在这儿，你也在这儿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了这些可以量化的具体事物之外，amount也可以用来描述抽象的事物，表示“程度”的意思。换句话说，行为或抽象事物其实也是可以量化的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">情感</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Her case has caught an enormous amount of public sympathy.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她的情况得到了无数公众的同情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I felt a certain amount of embarrassment.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我觉得有点尴尬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I do not love Joey. I like him a normal amount.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我不爱乔伊，我只是在正常范围内喜欢他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We love kids the appropriate amount.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们爱孩子，但恰如其分。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">言行</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">No amount of persuading could make her change her mind.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">怎么劝也无法让她改变主意。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">level</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">通常来讲，level会被翻译成“水平”，这其实已经是个引申出来的含义了。它的基础词义应该是“高度”。一个事物处在不同的高度，就拥有不同的level。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">高度</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">很多事物都要用高度来衡量。比如说，水的高度也就是水位是water level，我们经常说的海平面就是sea level。开车的人需要关注油位，就是fuel level。我们的建筑也会分不同的高度，也就是我们通常说的楼层了，除了可以用floor表示外，还可以用level表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">含量</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">level还经常用在医学检查上，我们去医院验血、验尿的时候其实就是查各项指标的level。比如血液里酒精的level，胆固醇的level，血糖的level等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">水平</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">最常用的抽象词义还是把它当“水平”讲，如我们的英语技能就分不同level，学习前要先测试你的level，是属于初级（beginner level），还是中级（intermediate level），当然最终都希望达到高级（advanced level）。另外，我们还经常说工资水平（salary level）、服务水平（level of service）、医疗水平（level of medical care）、战略水平（level of strategy）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">程度</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">另外，其他可以用数量来衡量的抽象概念都可以用level表示，如污染的程度（level of pollution），成就的大小（level of achievement），压力的大小（stress level）等。有人说了，这三个不是也可以用size来表示吗？没错，只不过level更加偏重于不同的层级，这也反映了英语表达的多样性。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">任何事物都有它的way</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">中国有句俗语叫“小鸡不尿尿，各有各的道”。这里的“道”其实就是指英语的way。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事物的形成和发展是有它固定的方式的，这就是form和way这两个词的含义。form主要是指事物形成的方式，也就是说它是如何形成的，并延伸为表示形成之后的样式。而way则是指事物发展的方式。下面重点介绍一下way这个词的用法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">way是英语口语中出现频率最高的名词之一，比如，在《老友记》中就出现过近1000次。它的用法也非常广泛，在朗文高阶词典中共有54个义项。那么，如何理解并记忆这些用法？还是要从其具体意义入手，找到统一的线索，然后再扩展到其抽象意义。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">way的原意是“道路”，指从一个地方到另一个地方必须经过的途径。若将此意引申开来，则是指世上的万事万物都有它存在、发展、实现的方式方法，所以，可以这样说，任何事物或任何行为都伴随着它的way，也就是说，way已成了事物的一个属性，这也是way在英语中应用如此广泛的原因。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有很多词是以way为原始词义生成的，表示某种行为方式和某件事的发展方式。先让我们来看看具体都有哪些。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">行为方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">behavior=the way that somebody behaves</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">tradition=a way of doing something that has existed for a long time among a group of people</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">style=the particular way in which something is done</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">感知方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">mood=the way you are feeling at a particular time</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">思考方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">logic=a way of thinking or explaining something</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">生活方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">culture=the way of life of a particular country or group</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">组织方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">order=the way in which people or things are arranged</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">structure=the way in which the parts of something connected together</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">pattern=the regular way in which something happened or is done</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">相处方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">relation=the way in which two people, groups deal with each other</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">说话方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">accent=a way of pronouncing the words of a language</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">上面的词汇全部可以用way做基础词来进行解释，而且很多可以直接用way来替代。有些词我们虽然很熟悉，如mood, order, logic等，但在让学员做单词释义练习的时候，他们却几乎想不到用way来解释，这说明我们对way这个词的了解和使用远远不够。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了上面这些生成词之外，很多具体的行为也都可以用way来表达它的方式。如下面这些句子，都是我们在课堂上用到的一些练习：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">吃东西的方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Kids always put food all over their faces. That's the way they eat.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">孩子们吃得满脸都是，他们就是这个样子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">扎头发的方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Miss Zhang always ties her hair up. That's her way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">张小姐总喜欢把头发扎起来。她就是这个样子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">工作的方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I don't like this way of working.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我不喜欢这种工作方式。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">拿剪刀的方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">That's not the right way to hold a pair of scissors.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">那样拿剪刀不对。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">示爱的方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She loves you in her own way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她以特有的方式爱着你。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">美丽的方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She is pretty, you're pretty too, but not in the same way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她很漂亮，你也很漂亮，但不是一种美。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了直接用way表达方式的意思之外，我们在课堂上还会从不同的角度对way的用法进行拓展，如与其他词的搭配等，这也是课堂训练经常会用到的方法。请看下面的例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第一，有没有way的问题。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">既然是“道路”，就存在着有没有的问题。我们最熟悉的表达方式就是：No way！与其相对应的就是“有”way，英语中是这样表达的：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Isnt there any way you can keep him?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">难道你没有什么可以留住他的办法吗？（要是你的好友被男朋友甩了，就可以用上这句话了。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Look, there's got to be a way we can work past this.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">听着，肯定有个办法能帮我们渡过这个难关。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">David seems to have a way with children.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">看起来大卫对付孩子很有一套。（这里用have a way就比be good at doing要地道得多。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There is no way around it.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">此事无解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There's no way he's moving back.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他绝不可能再搬回来。（与its impossible for him to move back比较一下，看哪个更口语化一些？）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">同样地，道路也存在着“找到”与“失去”的问题，如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">They got on the wrong trail and lost their way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他们走错了路，迷路了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I hope you can find some way to be happy for me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">希望你能看到值得为我高兴的地方。（当你做了某件很有成就感的事，而你的朋友却不很认同的时候，就可以用上这句话。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第二，是指哪一条way。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">“道路”有时候不止一条，需要指明，请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You cant have it both ways.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你不可能两样都占着。（汉语是说两样东西，在英语中则是从两个角度来看。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You're pretty much running that risk either way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">不管怎样，你都是在冒险。（either是我们不大习惯使用的词汇，在此与way搭配表示不管选哪一种方式。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Hes a good person, and in some ways I think he is so right for me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他是个好人，我想在某些方面很适合我。（这种情况经常出现在男女之间谈朋友上。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He makes out he's doing me a big favor, but actually it’s the other way around.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他声称是在帮我一个大忙，但实际上正好相反。（除了opposite这个词，其实用the other way around来表达会更加形象。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">That's the way to go！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">干得好！（除了keep it up、well done、good for you等表示鼓励的话语外，我们又多了一种表达方式。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm not at all surprised they feel that way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他们有那样的感受我一点不奇怪。（对同一件事情有什么样的feeling因人而异。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Let me put it this way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这么说吧！（这句话的意思是换一种方式来解释，也就等于把要说的东西“放到另一条路上”。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I've never looked at you that way before.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以前我还从来没这样看过你。（看一个人也可以从不同的角度。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I didn't want to get the part that way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我不想以那样的方式获取这个角色。（有人获取角色凭演技，有人则通过不正当手段，无论哪一种，都是不同的way。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Monica feels the same way that I do.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">莫妮卡和我有一样的感受。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Go your own way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">按你的想法来。（你有你的想法，其实就是你的way。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Have it your own way！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">随你便！（注意，这句话带有不耐烦的语气，用北方话说就是“你爱咋咋的吧！”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第三，是条什么样的way。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">“道路”有好坏，a good/bad way；也有正确与错误，a right/wrong way；还可以有a strange/friendly way，根据你具体想表达的意思采用不同的形容词来修饰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">当然，更多时候要说明这条路是什么人采用的，以及是用来做什么的。请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Look at the way hes dressed！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">看他穿成了什么样子！（衣服有不同的穿法，就是有不同的way。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Is this the way you get girls to go out with you?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这就是你哄小姑娘跟你约会的手法？（很实用的一句话哟！）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You use humor as a way of keeping people at a distance.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你的幽默是用来拒人于千里之外的。（这里的a way of用来解释手段。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Sometimes Tim needs to be alone. That's just the way he is.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有时候，吉姆需要一个人待着。他就是这么个人。（每个人都有自己的行为方式，只有这样，世界才丰富多彩。想想你的the way I am是什么？）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">If you want it typed, it's going to cost you. That's the way it is.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果你想把它打印出来，就得花钱。就是这样。（如果一件事是事实，没什么道理可讲的时候，你就可以用thats the way it is。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The chick was nice and crispy-just the way I like it.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">鸡肉又香又脆——正是我喜欢的那种。（之所以不能用kind来代替way，就是因为这儿的鸡不是指哪一个品种，而是特殊的味道。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第四，既然是条“路”，就有上有下，可与介词搭配使用。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">最常见的就是by the way了，我们都知道它的意思是“顺便说一下”，是个固定搭配。其实这个意思是可以从它的字面上读出来的，直译就是“在路边”，而不是“路的正中间”，自然就是顺带的事情了。再看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Ross‘s hands work their way down until they’re on Rachel's butt.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">罗斯的手一路摸下去，一直到瑞秋的臀部。（这是《老友记》中的一句话，work ones way是一个非常有用的表达方式。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">With him out of the way as my best friend, there's a spot open.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因为他已不再是我最好的朋友了，所以（最好的朋友）这个位置空缺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Platform shoes are on the way out.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">厚底鞋过时了。（“过时”我们常用out of fashion，如果用on the way out的话则带有一点正在过时的意思。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Forecasters say warmer weather is on the way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">预报员说天气就要暖和起来了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">way的用法还有很多，但只要你记住事物的发展都有它的way，并且以“路”的特征来理解和记住它，你就可以做到活学活用，丰富自己的表达方式。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\">\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h2 class=\"bodycontent-second-title\">有的单纯，有的世故——动词</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">英语中的动词是中国学习者比较头疼的部分，要么用错了，要么不会用。主要原因在于英语的动词和汉语的动词在构成的方式上有比较大的区别。区别在哪里呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">简单来说，就是英语中最基础的动词是可拆分的，而汉语的动词大部分是不可拆分的。换句话说，英语的一些动词是自由组合型的，可随时随地与其他词联手搏击，杀伤力很大。而汉语的动词则是抱团取暖型的，已是固定搭配，不能自由组合。所以，当抱团取暖型碰上自由组合型，必然会显得力量有余，灵活不足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">还是通过一些例子来说明吧！大家还记得下面这些词汇吗？前面给大家讲过：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">要求：request/ask for</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">报复：revenge/get back on</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">调查：investigate/look into</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">合作：cooperate/work together</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">取出：withdraw/take out</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">建立：establish/set up</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">削减：decrease/cut down</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">组装：assemble/put together</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">拒绝：reject/turn down</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">归还：return/give back</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">加速：accelerate/speed up</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上每一个汉语单词在英语中都对应着英语的两种表达方式，第一种是单独一个词，第二种是一个词组。也就是说，前面一组单独的词在英语中是可以拆分成两个词的组合的，组合中的第一个词表示动作，第二个词表示结果。但汉语却不可以进行这样的拆分，你把“要求”拆成“要”和“求”，把“报复”拆成“报”和“复”等是无法表达同样的意思的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">“一笑置之”怎么说？</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有人会说，不是还有一个单独的词可以用吗？干吗一定要拆分呢？问题就在于，并不是所有汉语中的词都有一个固定的英语单词与之对应，有相当一部分的表达是必须通过这种组合型的词组来表达的。如下面的句子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有关于他的流言蜚语，他只是一笑置之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话用英语要怎么说？你能不能帮我找到一个词专门是表达“一笑置之”的？查词典也行。查到了吗？它需要通过组合型的词组来表示，和上面的词组一样，“一笑置之”这个词也包括一个动作和一个结果，分别是laugh和off。所以，这句话就可以表达成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There was a rumor about him. He just laughed it off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">laugh这个词大家都会，但off大家就不一定想得到了。这个词也是学习者的软肋。我们有一堂课是专门学这个词的，因为这个词实在太有用了，无论是单打独斗，还是组合出击，都无所不能，后面讲介词的时候会跟大家讲。再举个例子，比如你想表达下面的意思：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他说谎不高明，任何人都能识破他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">“被人识破”怎么说？</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">同样地，你能否在词典里帮我找到一个单词是专门表达“识破”这个意思的？你还得把它拆分，分成动作和结果，动作就是see，结果是介词through。所以，这句话就说成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is a poor liar. Anybody can see through him.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，以上汉语动词有的自身也包含了行为和结果两层意思。如“取出”这个词中“取”就是动作，“出”就是结果，“建立”中“建”就是动作，“立”就是结果。这是汉语常用的一种造词方式，但因为这种用法已经约定俗成，单个字的本义已体现不出来了，所以就没办法像英语那样自由地拆分组合了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">通过以上分析可以看出，掌握英语中那些可以自由组合的动词以及经常与其搭配的介词是多么重要。所以，从这个角度出发，我把英语的动词分成了两大类，一类是“单纯型”动词，另一类是“世故型”动词，哈哈，听上去好玩吧。这种分法听上去虽然不是很严肃，但比较直观，也比较人性化，是不？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所谓的“单纯型动词”，顾名思义就是指那些“涉世不深，一眼就能看透”的词。这些词的词义非常简单，正因为单纯、不设防，所以可以和很多介词或其他词交上朋友，搭配表达出丰富的意义来。如put这个词，单看这个词没什么特别的意思，就是“放”，但它几乎可以和所有的介词结合表达出不同的意思来，如about, across, aside, at, away, back, down, forth, forward, in, off, on, out, through, together, up，等等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">“世故型动词”正好相反，是指那些看上去很“高深”，本身就很有“内涵”的词，因为它们自给自足，不愿意和别的词交朋友，所以用法上就比较单一。简单的如drown这个词是“淹死”的意思，既有动作“淹”，也有这个动作造成的结果“死”，所以，只需要说He was drowned in river.就可以了，没必要再加个“死”字上去。复杂一点的如afford这个词，它的词义是to have enough money to be able to buy something，一个词表达了三层意思，第一层是“有钱”，第二层是“有能力”，第三层是“买东西”。所以，我们只要说we can afford a car就可以了，而不用再提有没有钱，有没有能力的事。但是，虽然这两个词的能量很足，却不受其他词待见，因为基本上没有可以与它们搭配的词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们在前面的章节里也说过，一个意思往往会有两种表达方式，一种是比较直接的，用一个词就可以解决，就是指“世故型”的动词；另一种是用解释的方式，用的词虽然多一些，但更加具体，就是指这种“单纯型”的动词。这两种词的区别就好比我们想吃汉堡包，你可以花钱直接去麦当劳买一个，也可以用面包片、生菜、鸡肉、色拉等原料自己做一个，虽然费点时间，但一样能吃，说不定口感更好。因为我们的汉语词汇属于前者——现成汉堡包型的，所以掌握起“世故型”的动词来不是很难，但因为不是每一种口味的汉堡包麦当劳都会提供，所以我们更加需要掌握这种原料式的“单纯型”动词，用DIY的技术，随时随地，加工出自己想吃的口味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">单纯型动词：广交天下朋友</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">本源词</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">be go come make</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">归属</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">拥有某物　have</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">得到某物　get</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">给出某物　give</p></div>"
        },
