            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Id like to give you a lift.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我开车送你吧！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Can I take a lift?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我能搭个便车吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家通过上面的例句可以看出，即使不用这四个词，直接用它们后面的行为名词做谓语，也能表达同样的意思。这些例句进一步说明了，这四个词仅仅起到行为的指向作用，并没有具体的含义。这么用只是英语的一种习惯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小试牛刀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请大家用have, give, get, take这四个词与下面的事物轮流搭配使用，看看是否能理解其中的含义：</p></div>"
        },
