            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">单纯动词的不单纯用法</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">通过前面讲的make, go, have, give, get这几个词，大家应该已充分领略了单纯动词的魅力，它们不但能单打独斗，而且还能与其他词联手表达更丰富的内容。所以说，单纯动词只是看上去单纯，真正动起手来却是虎虎生风，武艺高强。可惜的是，因为汉语的特点，我们对这些单纯动词了解得太少，这是我们真正需要强化的地方。因章节有限，这里无法让大家了解更多的单纯动词，只能简单地做个总结。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">对单纯动词的认识太单一，很多词连基本的用法都没学会。举例来说：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">流鼻涕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">拉伤肌肉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">崴了脚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">破了皮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">伤口愈合</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">发动汽车</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">压低嗓音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">管用</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">别挤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上都是我们在生活中经常用到的，不过我相信里面没几个是大家可以一下说出来的。其实都是很简单的词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My nose is running.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">pull ones muscle</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">turn ones ankle</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The skin breaks.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The wound is closing.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Start the car.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Drop your voice.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It works.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Don't push.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">再举个例子，比如，我们描述下面这样一个用水浇花的过程：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">从井（well）里打出水来，用水管（pipe）把它送到水龙头（tap），把水龙头打开放水，然后用桶（barrel）接住，再将桶里的水浇到花上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">就这么一小段，估计没几个人能够准确地把其中的动词表达出来。其实都是我们表中的那些单纯的行为动词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Draw water from the well, carry it with pipe, turn on the tap to run the water, catch it with a barrel, spread the water over the plant.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">不仅仅是具体的事物，一些行为和事件也可以与这些单纯动词搭配使用，如game，你可以有下面这些表达：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">start a game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">开始比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">hold the game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">暂停比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">quit a game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">退出比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">lose a game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">输掉比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">throw a game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">故意输掉比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">take a game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">赢下比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">fix a game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">操纵比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">turn a game</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">扭转比赛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">抽象概念也可以与这些词搭配，如concentration这个词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">break ones concentration</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">分散某人的注意力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">catch ones concentration</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">抓住某人的注意力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">draw ones concentration</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">吸引某人的注意力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">lose ones concentration</p></div>"
