        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">锁定某人的注意力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">单纯词与其他词搭配能有效地解决一些世故词无法表达的东西。比如下面的一些表达：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他转而把气撒到狗身上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他试图让我妹妹掉头反对我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他看上去和其他孩子不大合群。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个产品能帮我们打开上海市场。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">只有两天假期可以延到下一年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们的报告是今天早上才匆匆写成的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他因为与老师顶嘴惹下了麻烦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上句子很难找到某一个具体的动词把谓语部分准确地说明白，但如果用我们词表中的单纯动词加上一些介词就可以轻松地解决：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He turned the anger on his dog.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He tried to turn my sister against me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He doesn't seem to fit in with the other children.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This product will help us to break into Shanghai market.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Only two day of vacation can be carried over into next year.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Our report was thrown together this morning.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He got in trouble for talking back to his teacher.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这就是单纯词的魅力，正因为它们单纯，所以可以和其他词自由组合，表达世故词表达不了的东西，到达世故词到达不了的领域。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家是否都玩过一个叫“俄罗斯方块”的小游戏？世故词就像是俄罗斯方块中的七种形状，每一种都由四个小正方形按不同的形状组成，所以都会有自己无法嵌进去的地方。而单纯词就好比那个最小的小正方形，无论什么地方都能嵌进去，所以作用最大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000001951",
