        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">关于世故型动词的解读</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">总单词量：219个</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">类别：14个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">世故型动词主要是根据人的不同行为来分类的。这种分类有助于我们对近似的行为有一个大概的了解，并能帮助我们在需要的时候以最快的速度在这一类别中找到所需要的词。在上篇中已举例说明，我们的培训课程也是按照这种分类进行授课的，此处不再多言。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">前面介绍过，世故型动词就是指那些包含信息比较多的动词。因为它们自身包含的信息多，所以就不大需要用那些表示位置、力量、方向等的副词和介词来修饰，可与它们搭配的词就比较少，相应地，它们的用途比单纯型动词也要少。但是，正因为它们不需要别人配合，所以它们的独立性比较强，经常是一个词顶好几个词，这是它们的优点。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">对我们来说，既要学好单纯词以便掌握更灵活的表达方式，也要在这个基础上尽可能多地掌握世故型词汇，以使自己的表达更简单、更富有变化。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面我就以suffer和enjoy为例，说明世故型动词的作用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">享受还是遭罪</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">enjoy和suffer两个词都属于世故词，且词义相反。从上下义词的关系来说，它们两个都是单纯词have的下义词。也就是说，这两个词都有have的词义，但have的东西却不一样。我们看看词典中对这两个词的解释：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">enjoy：to have something that is good to you</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer：to have something that is bad to you</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一个是have好的东西，一个是have坏的东西，正好完全相反。所以，我们可以简单地划分一下，如果你have的是对你有利的东西，那就可以用enjoy来代替，如果你have的东西是对你不利的，那就用suffer来代替。我们来看看一些具体的搭配：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">enjoy</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">enjoy home advantages　拥有主场优势</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">enjoy grass roots support　有草根支持</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">enjoy super ability　享有超能力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">enjoy good health　享有健康</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">enjoy a good reputation　有好名声</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
