        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">suffer</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer a cough　咳嗽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer headache　头疼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer a fever　发烧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer punishment　受惩罚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer a loss　蒙受损失</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer air pollution　遭受空气污染</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer an earthquake　遭受地震</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer a car accident　遇到车祸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer a fire　遭受火灾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">suffer poor service　得到糟糕的服务</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上表达其实都可以用have来代替，但是，当它们分别用enjoy或suffer来代替的时候，听的人就会更清楚你说话的角度。这就是世故词所起的作用，通俗地说，它会让你的表达感觉更有“范儿”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因为世故型动词与汉语的词组比较相似，所以大部分世故型动词与汉语的词汇存在着词义上的对应关系，比如design对应着“设计”，immigrate对应着“移民”，arrange对应着“安排”，反过来也大同小异。所以对学员来说，大多数的世故型动词掌握来比起变化多端的单纯型动词要容易得多，但仍有一些特殊的情况需要我们特别掌握。下面就分别举例说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">两词并一词</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">世故型动词中有一些词的涵盖能力非常强，如在本章节开始介绍的afford这个词，同时包含了三个动词的意思，与我们汉语有着比较大的差别。这类词在英语中不在少数，且使用频率非常高，所以需要我们给予特别的重视。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">再举两个最常见的例子，try和want。这两个词大家都很熟悉，但不是每一个人都能做到灵活运用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这两个词的共同特点是它们的语义都非常强烈，以至于经常可以把它们后面的动词省略掉，直接与名词搭配。如我们表达以下两个意思：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们试着推了推门，但锁上了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你想听我的建议吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">通常情况下，这两句话会被我们说成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We tried to push the door, but it was locked.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Do you want to hear my advice?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">但口语中这两句话说得就更简洁了：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We tried the door, but it was locked.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Do you want my advice?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上两句分别省掉了不定式中的push和hear两个动词。能够省掉的主要原因是，这两个动词在句子中的作用已不明显，因为它们表达了两个常识性的东西：“门通常是用来推的”，而“意见通常是用来听的”，这也符合英语表达中“能省就省”的原则。请看这两个词更多的例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You can try her mobile phone.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你可以打她手机试试。（省略了to call）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Would you like to try my soup?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">要不要尝尝我做的汤？（省略了to taste）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I tried six stores before I found the book.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我跑了6家书店才找到那本书。（省略了to go to）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I want his gift for my birthday.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">生日那天我想收到他的礼物。（省略了to receive）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I want your promise.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我希望你能下个保证。（省略了to make）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She wants a baby.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她想生个孩子。（省略了to give birth to）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了这两个词比较典型外，还有其他一些词也具备这样的特点。如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">start</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The children start school next week.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">孩子们下周开学。（省略了to go to）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Let's start a new bottle of wine！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">让我们新开一瓶葡萄酒吧！（省略了to drink）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Its time to start your homework.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">到开始做作业的时间了。（省略了to do）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">expect</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm expecting a call from him.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我期望能接到他的电话。（省略了to receive）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">How many visitors are you expecting?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你希望能有多少人来访？（省略了to come）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Don't expect sympathy from me！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">别指望从我这儿得到同情！（省略了to give）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">自己飞还是让别人飞？</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">世故型动词还有另外一个常见的现象，就是有些词既可以做不及物动词也可以做及物动词。因为我们往往只熟悉其中的一种用法，所以就会忽略另一种用法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">举例来说，fly这个词，我们最先学习的就是“飞”的意思，比如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The bird is flying.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小鸟在飞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The kite is flying.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">风筝在飞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">在这两句话中，fly都是不及物动词，但事实上，fly还可以做及物动词，表示“让……飞”的意思。所以，想表达“放风筝”这个意思的时候，就不需要说：make the kite fly，而直接说成：fly the kite，省力很多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">而有的词我们则熟悉它们做及物动词的用法，如write，我们会说：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm writing a letter.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我在写信。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">但write也完全可以用作不及物动词，不需要带宾语，如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This pen wont write.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这笔写不出字来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小试牛刀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面给出更多的例子，看看大家能否猜出它们做不及物动词时候的意思来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The water is boiling.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Boil the water.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is working.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is working the coffee machine.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The shoes hurt me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The shoes hurt.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The hot coffee burns my mouth.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The coffee burns.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This sweater washes well.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Wash clothes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My company pays me a lot of money.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My company pays well.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Copying will cost you a lot of money.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Copying costs.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He shares everything with me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Kids don't share.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">“盐”就是“腌”的意思</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">英语中还有一类比较常见的世故型动词，我们在词表中并没有列出来。那就是直接把名词拿来用作动词。这种情况非常多，有些我们也经常用，比如rain，既可以当名词用表示“雨水”，也可以当动词用表示“下雨”。dream，既可以当名词用表示“梦”，也可以当动词用意思是“做梦”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">但还有一些是我们以前没用过，但却很实用的。比如salt，当名词用是“盐”的意思，但完全可以直接拿来当动词用，表示“腌”的意思，不需要再加其他句子成分。其实很好理解，“腌”东西不就得用盐嘛！所以，你就可以说成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Salt the fish.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">把鱼腌起来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这种用法最大的好处就是节省了动词，我们不用费心再另外找一个动词了。类似的名词非常多，举例如下：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Water the plants.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">给花浇浇水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He colored his dog red.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他把狗染成了红色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He pocketed the changes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
