        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">typical normal common general popular average particular own</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">重要性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">serious causal important main formal professional</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">必要性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">necessary</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">关联性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">free relative legal physical mental local native international cheap expensive separate public worth</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">关于形容词的解读总单词量：208个</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">类别：47个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">根据牛津词典的统计，形容词的数量仅次于名词，约占词汇总数的四分之一，比动词多出将近一倍。但在我们的R词汇表里，形容词不但没有动词多，甚至比它还要少三分之一。因为我们根本不需要掌握那么多，只要把形容词里面最基础、最不可或缺的学到就可以了。为什么呢？其实通过词表的分类大家已可以看得很清楚了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家都知道，形容词是用来修饰名词的，所以，首先，我们只要根据名词的分类把各个类别中最重要的形容词找出来就可以了。根据前面名词的介绍，表示事物的名词主要分为物、人和事，所以我们的形容词也是根据这三类来分的，这可以保证每一类事物都能找到与其对应的形容词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其次，我们描述事物主要是从两方面进行的，一是描述事物的属性，二是描述它的构成。所以，在每一个大类中又根据事物某一方面的属性和构成进行了更小的分类。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">描述属性的形容词比较容易理解，如表示事物“大小”“高低”“深浅”“长短”“粗细”的形容词都是用来描述不同事物尺寸的，而“方位”“距离”“正斜”这几类形容词都是用来描述事物的位置和方向的，“难度”“可能性”等则是用来描述事物发展的方式，而“真实性”“复杂性”这几类形容词则是用来描述事物的状态。品质类的形容词最多，就是用来描述事物在某一方面品质的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">而描述事物构成的形容词则相对不是很容易理解，要先知道这些形容词所指的具体组成是什么，如下面这些词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">描述物的组成</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有热量（heat）：hot warm cold cool</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有水分（water）：dry wet</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有光线（light）：bright dark dull</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有声音（sound）：loud noisy</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">描述人或动物的组成</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有食物（food）：hungry</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有水分（water）：thirsty</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有疾病（disease）：ill</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有孩子（baby）：pregnant</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有信心（confidence）：confident</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是否有金钱（money）：rich poor</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">构成类的形容词有个特点，就是说这些词大部分可以用“there be”或者“somebody/something have”句型加上具体的组成来代替。如下面这几个用形容词表述的句子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The cake is dry.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The room is dark.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is ill.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She is pregnant.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is rich.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">上面这几个句子都可以用它们具体表述的组成事物water, light, disease, baby, money分别改成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There's not much water in the cake.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There's little light in the room.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He has a disease.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She has a baby in the stomach.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He has a lot of money.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个特点为我们的表达提供了另外一个选择，可以在我们不知道或忘记这一类形容词的时候用其他句子表达，等会儿再具体说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">天生的形容词就那几个</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">好了，对我们这个R词汇表做了一个简单的了解之后，我们就要说明一下为什么只需要这些形容词就够了。主要和形容词的生成方式有很大的关系，形容词虽然总量非常大，但它的生成方式和原因主要包括以下几种：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">一、大部分形容词是从其他词生成的，可在学习其他词的时候一并学习。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">天生就是形容词的词并不多，有相当一部分是从名词和动词加上后缀派生出来的。如下面这些词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">名词生成的形容词</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">构成类的形容词，表示有或无</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有一些：bloody cloudy windy skinny stormy tricky dirty</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有很多：careful useful powerful hopeful fruitful helpful colorful skillful</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">没有：careless useless powerless hopeless fruitless helpless homeless worthless</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">属性类的形容词，表示状态或某种属性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">像什么：foolish childish selfish girlish ladylike bird like businesslike</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">具备某种属性：traditional social cultural accidental magical logical practical political historical</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">动词生成的形容词</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">表示某种能力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">exciting surprising interesting relaxing alarming amazing attractive</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">表示某种状态</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">excited surprised interested relaxed alarmed frozen limited related</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上形容词都是在我们熟悉的名词或动词的基础上加上一定形式的后缀形成的，很容易掌握，所以，根本没必要把它们作为一个单独的形容词进行记忆。我们在教学中会在学习其他词汇的时候一并讲解如何掌握这些派生出来的形容词，同时也作为思维转换的一种训练方式。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">二、有些词只是为了让描述更精确，只要用程度副词来修饰一下就可以。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们知道，与用数量进行的精确描述相比，形容词对事物的属性描述是比较宽泛的，一般只有两个选择，如big和small, good和bad, deep和shallow等，分别代表属性的两个方向。但是，有时候仅用这两个单词会显得比较单调，需要发明出表达程度更强的词来。以good和bad为例，光说“好”或“坏”还不够，还要体现出“很好”和“很坏”来，所以在good的基础上又分别生成了great, wonderful, fabulous，在bad的基础上又生成了awful, terrible等，一个比一个程度更深。出于类似需要生成的词还有很多：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">big（大）　huge（庞大）　giant（巨大）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">small（小）　mini（袖珍）　slight（一点）　tiny（极小）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">beautiful（漂亮）　gorgeous（太漂亮了）　stunning（绝美）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">strange（奇怪）　unusual（有点奇怪）　bizarre（非常奇怪）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">silly（傻）　stupid（很傻）　ridiculous（太傻了）　absurd（荒唐）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">scary（吓人的）　horrible（可怕的）　creepy（毛骨悚然的）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这些词虽然能对我们的口语表达起到增姿增彩的作用，但对level较低的学员来说，现阶段还没必要掌握那么多。事实上，我们只要从每个属性中找出最基本的两个来，然后用a little, very和extremely三个副词修改一下就可以起到相同的效果。比如ridiculous就是very silly的意思，而absurd就是extremely silly的意思，只要记住silly就可以了，完全不需要再学ridiculous和absurd这两个词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">三、有些词只是表达了事物的“有”或“无”，可用have或there be句型代替。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如前所述，有的形容词是用来说明某种事物是否存在的。对这类词我们只要找出所说的事物并以解释的方式用there be或have句式来表达就可以。如以下词汇，加粗的字是变通的说法：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">numb（麻木的）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My leg is numb.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My leg doesn't have feeling.或者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My leg lost its feeling.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">naked（裸体的）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She is naked.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There're no clothes on her.或者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She doesn't wear any clothes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">anonymous（匿名的）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">an anonymous letter</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">a letter without the writers name</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">四、有些词是比较书面的语言，可用口语化的词汇代替。如下面这些词：</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">书面语 口语</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">intelligent smart</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">remote far</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">significant important</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">ultimate final</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">wealthy rich</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">artificial fake</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">conscious aware</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">entire whole</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">various different</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这样的词对学习者来说并不容易区分，同样需要老师在授课时给予明确的讲解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">“画挂歪了”要怎么说？</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与动词一样，大部分学习者对形容词的认识也是严重不足。动词分为单纯词和世故词，形容词也可以这样来分。形容词中的单纯词是指那些描述“物”的词，如big, heavy, hot, strong等，而世故词则主要是指另两类，描述“人”的，如busy, happy, smart等，描述“事”的，如difficult, impossible, effective等。对于后两类，大家一般都还能掌握，因为它们的词义变化并不是很大，而且和汉语的用法也差不多，只要背下来就可以。真正难的是对那些描述“物”的形容词的掌握。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这些单纯词看上去很简单，但正因为它们“单纯”，往往被我们忽视。最突出的问题有两个，我们下面分别说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第一，对这些单纯词的具体词义掌握不够。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所谓“具体词义”就是指这些词的本义，不是指后来延伸出来的那些意思。不信的话我们先来做个测试吧！请大家用英语表达下面几句话：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他嘴巴很大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这肉咬不动。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">挑结实的西红柿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我领带正不正？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这鞋子有点挤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">画挂歪了。</p></div>"
