        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">high summer</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">正午</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">high noon</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">茂密的森林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">a thick forest</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">怎么样？这些词都认识吧？但就是这么简单的词，别说是初学者，就是过了专业八级的也未必都能一口气说出来。这么说并非不敬，而是因为我们传统的英语教学对这一块重视不够。想象一下，如果我们在工作和生活中与老外交流时连这些话都要想半天，确实需要反思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上仅仅举了几个典型的例子，生活中大量常见的实例，都是可以用这些看似单纯的形容词来解决的。就拿说话的声音为例，我们一般会分为“低低的声音”“响亮的声音”“尖细的声音”“粗重的声音”“温柔的声音”“沙哑的声音”“坚定的声音”等，可以分别用a low voice, a high voice, a thin voice, a thick voice, a soft voice, a rough voice, a firm voice这些单纯的形容词来表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">或许你觉得这个不够实用，写作文的时候才能用上，那就再举个实用的例子，比如我们天天要喝的饮料。“软饮料”要怎么说，“高度酒”要怎么说，“低度酒”要怎么说，“可乐跑气了”要怎么说，“浓茶”要怎么说，“不加奶的咖啡”要怎么说，“不加冰的威士忌”要怎么说，“难喝的酒”要怎么说，“口感顺滑的酒”要怎么说？其实还是用这些简单的形容词，分别表示为soft drink, hard liquor, light wine, the cola is flat, strong tea, black coffee, straight whiskey, rough wine, smooth and rich wine，等等。你陪外国友人去酒吧的时候总得知道一些常用的说法，不能老是用good, bad来表达吧？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面再给大家列出其他一些典型的例子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">full name　全名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">full moon　满月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">thin hair　稀疏的头发</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">rough skin　粗糙的皮肤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">rough track　崎岖难走的路</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
