        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">flat tire　瘪了气的轮胎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">“老板很抠门”要怎么说？</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第二，对这些单纯词的抽象词义了解得更少。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们先看看以下这些我们在工作和生活中经常会用到的对人或对事的描述。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他这个人很抠门。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他这个人自以为了不起。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他和老同学聚会的时候感觉很自卑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他很有城府，谁也不信任。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">老板成天板着个脸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他的观点比较狭隘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他说的都是空话。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">老板是个不讲情面的人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是一个团结的群体。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">没了你，我生活很空虚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">最近几个月房产市场不景气。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们的进度太赶了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">怎么样？都是平时的大白话吧？看上去很难吧？估计这次把时间给足你也很难找到正确的表达方式，因为上面的很多形容词你都没有单独学过，或者说没有背到过。事实上，不是没学过，只是我们没意识到而已。还是要用那些单纯词汇来表达：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他这个人很抠门。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is tight with money.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他这个人自以为了不起。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is so full of himself.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他和老同学聚会的时候感觉很自卑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He feels small when he is with his old classmates.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他很有城府，谁也不信任。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is a deep one, trusting nobody.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">老板成天板着个脸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Our boss keeps a straight face all day.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他的观点比较狭隘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He has a narrow view.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他说的都是空话。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He speaks only empty words.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">老板是个不讲情面的人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Our boss is a hard man.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是一个团结的群体。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This is a tight group.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">没了你，我生活很空虚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I feel empty without you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">最近几个月房产市场不景气。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The housing market is flat for months.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们的进度太赶了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We have a tight schedule.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">听上去那么难的表达，说起来却很简单。为什么会这样呢？其实很好理解，这和语言的比喻功能分不开。我们前面曾经教过大家一个技巧，就是“拣实心的”，单纯词就是实心词，是我们平时描述身边的具体事物时离不开的，但它们完全可以引申出来表达抽象的含义。这就是人类智慧的体现，就像我们标题所说的，学形容词，就要让感觉飞起来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">我们生活在一个沉重的世界</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">举个例子吧！比如heavy这个词，大家都知道是“重”的意思，不过这可能也是大家唯一会用的意思，实际上在朗文词典中，它的词义和用法多达32种。但其他31种都是从“重”这个词义引申出来的。是怎么引申的呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002412": {
