            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这车耗油量大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">天气</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It's very heavy, I think there’ll be a storm.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">天气很闷，估计要下暴雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">态度</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Don't be so heavy on her.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">不要对她那么苛刻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">心情</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He went home with a heavy heart.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他心情沉重地回到家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家可以看出，从经济到工作，从生活用品到日常行为，从态度到心理，原本需要用很多其他词来表达的事物，通过一个简单的比喻就几乎都被heavy给覆盖了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其实不仅仅是英语，所有的语言都会用这种比喻的手法。如汉语中，我们前面举的那些例子，很多都是带“重”字的，如“沉重”“浓重”“繁重”“重大”“粗重”等，只是因为我们除了“重”字外，还另外加了一个有所侧重的词，使得这些词脱离了原始的词义，变成了另外一个新的词，所以才会造成我们在想表达此类意思的时候不能马上想到用heavy。因此，我们要想学好这个词的用法，就必须针对这个词进行反复的搭配训练，直到我们在需要用这个词的时候能快速反应出来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">heavy这个词大家比较熟悉，再挑两个大家相对比较陌生却又比较实用的词讲讲它们的神奇妙用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">sharp</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">sharp的初始词义是“锋利的，尖利的”，一般用来形容刀具。锋利的刀具通常会给人带来三种感觉：一是切割东西比较快，用时短；二是容易伤到人；三是切割面比较整齐、鲜明。sharp的抽象用法主要就是在这三种感觉上形成的，请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">相貌</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Mia has a sharp nose.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">米娅的鼻子又高又尖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">声音</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">A sharp cry of pain.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">痛苦的尖叫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">感觉</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I felt a sharp pain in my back.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我感到背部一阵剧痛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">言语</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She has a sharp tone.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她说话尖酸刻薄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We were surprised by the sharp tone of her comments.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她尖锐的评论让我们吃惊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">图像</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This TV set gives you a very sharp picture.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这台电视机图像非常清晰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">时间</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We‘re meeting at 10 o’clock sharp.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们要在10点整见面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">移动</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We came to a sharp turn in the road.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们来到了公路的急转弯处。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">价格</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">A sharp rise in price.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">价格的急剧上涨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">观察</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The job requires someone with a sharp eye for detail.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">做这项工作要有观察入微的眼力。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">rough</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">rough的初始词义是“粗糙的”。“粗糙”给人带来的感觉主要有两个，一是不舒服，二是不细致、不精确。请看以下例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Can you give me a rough idea of what courses I have to take?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你能大致告诉我要选些什么课程吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I've got a rough idea of where I want to go.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我有个大概的想法要去哪儿了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Look, if you wanna see some rough numbers, I can get them to you by Wednesday.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果你只想看个大概的数字，周三我就可以给你。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I've had a rough day.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我这一天过得糟透了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I had a rough night.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我一夜没睡好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The last years have been rough on wine producers.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">过去几年对葡萄酒厂家来说不是好年景。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Traveling thousands of miles in a small car was pretty rough.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">坐着小型车旅行数千里实在是太难受了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Were going through a rough time.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们正经历一段艰难的时光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因为这些单纯词的比喻作用，它们还可以对同一个事物用不同的单纯词与其搭配，比如下面几个主题。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">schedule</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">tight schedule　紧凑的行程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">heavy schedule　繁忙的行程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">loose schedule　宽松的行程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">rough schedule　大概的行程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">life</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">easy life　轻松的生活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">hard life　艰难的生活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">rough life　困苦的生活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">full life　充实的生活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">empty life　空虚的生活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">loose life　放荡的生活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">bitter life　悲惨的生活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">mind</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">great mind　有见识的头脑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">dirty mind　肮脏的头脑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">blank mind　大脑空白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">strong mind　意志坚强</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">open-minded　心态开放</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">narrow-minded　心胸狭隘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这样的搭配可以帮助我们熟悉这些单纯形容词的用法，在我们的训练课上会经常用到，有时候会搭配出一些意想不到的效果来，挺有意思的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">除了可以直接表达抽象的含义外，很多单纯词也可以用来代替其他抽象词汇，我们前面介绍bad的用法时就列举了很多。下面再以big为例，看看它的能量有多大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is a big decision.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是一个重要决定。（代替important）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You are making a big mistake.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你犯了一个严重的错误。（代替serious）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Do you really think we can take on the big boys?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你认为我们能够和这些高手对抗吗？（代替powerful）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">They're full of big ideas.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他们有很多野心勃勃的想法。（代替ambitious）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Orange is the big color this year.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">橙色是今年的流行色。（代替popular）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The band is very big in Japan.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个乐队在日本很成功。（代替successful）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm a big fan of hers.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我是她的超级粉丝。（代替enthusiastic）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He gave me an extra five pounds for two hours' work. I thought‘That's big of you’.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">两小时工作他又给我加了我5英镑，我想，哦，你很大方。（代替generous）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其他的还有：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You're too hard on Monica.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你对莫妮卡太严厉了。（代替strict）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Bob was giving her a hard time about her new boyfriend.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">鲍勃开她新男友的玩笑，让她很难堪。（代替embarrass）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Competition for the best jobs is getting hot.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一流职位的竞争越来越激烈了。（代替fierce）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The White House seems blind to the struggles of the middle class.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">白宫好像对中产阶级的挣扎视而不见。（代替ignore）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is clear that the drug does benefit some patients.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">很明显，这种药对一些病人有效。（代替obvious）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Everyone wants a clean and honest election.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">每个人都希望选举公平和公正。（代替fair）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I made only a few small changes to the report.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我只是对报告做了小小的调整。（代替slight）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小试牛刀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请大家试着理解以下句子中形容词的抽象含义，然后对照词典看你的理解是否正确。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is a little bit slow.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The roads were very clear this morning.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Children need a good, solid education in high school.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I have clean driving records.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She has thick, beautiful hair.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My chest was tight.</p></div>"
        },
