            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">than as</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">整体与部分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">besides among except including</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因果</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">according to</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">despite per</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">关于介词的解读</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">总单词量：48个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">类别：14个</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">介词主要是按照它们的功能进行分类的。我们需要重点学习的是前两大类：表示动态位置的介词和静态位置的介词。前者的用法比后者更多，这在后面会有具体的说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与名词、动词、形容词这三大词相比，介词在R词汇表中的数量是最少的，只有区区几十个。但就这区区几十个介词，却在英语的表达中占据了重要的位置。重要在哪里呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第一，使用频率高。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以大家最熟悉的《英语900句》为例，900个句子中有一半以上用到了介词。这个统计还是基于900句多为10个单词以下的短句做出的，对10个单词以上的长句来说，则几乎离不开介词穿针引线。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">第二，使用范围广。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">介词除了用于名词前表示方位外，大多可与动词搭配构成短语动词。以out为例，它可以与多达600个动词搭配构成短语动词。也就是说，仅仅一个介词就可以扩充出多达600个短语。如果再把每个短语动词所代表的一个以上的语义计算进去，则其应用就更加可观。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">可以毫不夸张地说，介词就是英语的灵魂，上与名词称兄道弟，下与动词拉帮结派，中间还经常和形容词勾勾搭搭。按中国的文化，它就是韦小宝式的角色，几乎没有它搞不定的事情。只有掌握了这个关键的灵魂人物，才算是真正掌握了英语这门语言。但可惜的是，学员们对介词的认识仅仅局限在“时间”和“地点”上，大把更实用的用法却被丢在一旁，就好比是拿了把尚方宝剑当拐棍用，太可惜了！可惜在哪儿呢？我们下面就来做个分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">单纯动词的神仙眷侣</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">一、与单纯动词搭配，让表达更形象、更准确</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">前面说过，单纯动词很容易和别的词交上朋友，介词就是它最好的朋友之一。两者经常联手出击，配合默契，发挥各自优势，解决了很多保守的世故词解决不了的问题。我们讲单纯词的时候举过下面两个例子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有关于他的流言蜚语，他只是一笑置之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There was a rumor about him, he just laughed it off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他说谎不高明。任何人都能识破他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is a poor liar. Anybody can see through him.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上两个句子中，off和through都起到了重要的配合作用。一个补充说明了laugh的结果，一个强调了see的路径。如果把单纯动词比作福尔摩斯的话，那么介词就是他的黄金搭档华生，一拆一解，问题搞定。再举更多的例子给大家，先看下面几句汉语表达，都是无法只用一个动词来解决的：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他爬过墙头。（“爬”用climb，“过”要怎么说？）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们正顶着风跑步。（“跑”用run，“顶”要怎么说？）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她最终说服我打消了买车的念头。（“说服”可以用convince，“打消”怎么办？）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">妈妈供养我上完大学，我对此心存感激。（“供养”可以用supply，“上完”怎么办？）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你可以把问题细分成三个部分以方便解决。（“细分”可以用break，“成”怎么办？）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">对这些一个动词解决不了的问题，都需要出动“单纯动词+介词”这对黄金组合，分别表达为：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She climbed over the wall.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Were running against the wind.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She finally talked me out of buying a new car.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm grateful to my mother for putting me through college.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You can break the question down into three parts to make it easier.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家可以很清楚地看到，以上句子中over, against, out of, through, into这几个介词在其中起到了穿针引线的作用。再把前面讲解单纯词时举过的例子放在下面，供大家一起比较体会：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他转而把气撒到狗身上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他试图让我的妹妹掉头反对我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他看上去和其他孩子不大合得来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个产品能帮我们打开上海市场。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">只有两天假期可以延到下一年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们的报告是今天早上才匆匆写成的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他因为与老师顶嘴惹下了麻烦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">分别用“单纯动词+介词”结构表达为：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He turned the anger on his dog.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He tried to turn my sister against me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He doesn't seem to fit in with the other children.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This product will help us to break into Shanghai market.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Only two day of vacation can be carried over into next year.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Our report was thrown together this morning.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He got in trouble for talking back to his teacher.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">二、代替动词</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们知道，介词主要是用来表达空间位置的，而动词主要是表达事物的移动和变化的。而有一些介词本身就表达了位置的变化，尤其是R词汇表中表达轨迹的一些词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">across　从一边到另一边</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">along　从一端到另一端</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">over　从一个点到另一个点</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">past　经过某一个点</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">through　穿过</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">off　下来</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">against　相抵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">它们的汉语意思本来就与动词的表达比较相近，所以就可以直接在句子中代替我们汉语中的动词。如下面的例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">衬衫外面再套个外套会使她看上去更好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她乘船横渡大西洋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">兔子穿过一个洞进了房间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们能听到金属互相摩擦的声音。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他骑自行车的时候双手脱把。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上句子中的套、横渡、穿过、摩擦、脱把这几个汉语中的动词分别可以用介词over, across, through, against, off来代替：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">A coat over that shirt makes her look great.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She took a ship across the Atlantic.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Rabbits got into the room through a hole.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We could hear the noise of metal against metal.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He rides bicycle with his hands off the handle.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">一个介词省掉一个句子</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">三、代替句子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">仅仅代替动词还不能完全体现出介词的超能量，英语的空间化特征使得整整一个句子都可以用“介词+名词”结构来解决。请看下面的汉语：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你上班的时候都干些啥？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我边吃早饭边看报纸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她睡觉的时候开着窗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他们俩都感冒了，双双卧病在床。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">经过再三考虑，我决定接受这个报价。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">穿白衣服的那位女士是谁？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">尽管她有不少缺点，我依然爱她。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">看到她的第一眼我就爱上了她。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你打电话6609823就能找到我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">上面这些句子我们通常会用“主句+从句”的形式表达成下面这个样子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">What do you do when you're working?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I read newspaper when I'm having breakfast.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The windows are open when she is sleeping.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">They've both got flu and lied in bed.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I will accept the offer after I think about it for a long time.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Who is the lady that wears white clothes?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Even though she has many faults, I still love her.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He fell in love with her when he first saw her.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You can reach me if you call 6609823.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">但老外的表达却往往是下面这个样子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">What do you do at work?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I read the newspaper over breakfast.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She sleeps with the window open.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">They're both in bed with flu.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">On second thoughts, I will accept the offer.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Who is the lady in white?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">With all her faults I still love her.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He fell in love with her at first sight.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You can reach me at 6609823.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">单从字数上看就比我们的表达要简短很多，显得更加简洁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">句子的“大管家”</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">四、理顺句型结构</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">对我们来说，前面介绍的介词的几个作用都还不是最重要的。最重要的是，英语的介词帮我们彻底理顺了英语的句子结构，使得我们在说英语的时候变得有序可循。这是被我们的学习者以及传统的英语教学严重忽视的一点。掌握了这一点，可以快速地掌握英语的语感，大大地缩短从哑巴英语到开口的时间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有这么神奇吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我先通过两个例句来说明一下英语的基本句型结构是什么样的：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I go to school by bike.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我骑自行车上学。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I was late for work yesterday.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我昨天上班迟到了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我希望大家比较一下上面两个句子中，中文和英文在语序上的差别。看出来了吗？区别在哪里？为了便于大家看清楚，我把它们的句子成分写在下面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">英语：I go to school by bike.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">主语谓语动词介词结构（目的地）介词结构（方式）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">汉语：我骑自行车上学。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">主语方式谓语</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">英语：I was late for work yesterday.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">主语谓语介词结构（目的地）时间状语</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">汉语：我昨天上班迟到了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">主语时间状语目的地谓语</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家看明白了吗？主要区别就在于，英语都是把谓语放在主语之后，处在第二位置，而汉语则是把谓语放在了最后，主语和谓语中间间隔着状语等其他成分。这种区别并不是偶然的，我们给出更多的例子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他们用树枝搭了个房子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">They made a house with branches.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们顶着风跑步。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Were running against the wind.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她手里提着个购物袋走了过来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She comes with a shopping bag in her hands.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">火车准时到达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The train arrived on time.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他们用英语交流。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">They talk in English.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我和我的一个朋友结了婚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I was married to a friend of mine.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家可以尝试一下，如果把汉语句子中的谓语像英语那样放在主语的后面，根本行不通，因为这是我们的思维习惯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">汉语和英语的这个区别经常会造成我们在表达上的混乱或者与地道的英语产生明显区别。比如前面的两句话，我们就有可能说成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I ride bike to go to school.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I went to work yesterday and was later.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">对照地道的英语表达，上面两句就显得有些拖泥带水。这两句比较短，即使费点劲还能勉强表达出来，但碰到比较长的，成分比较多的句子，像“她手里提着个购物袋走了进来”，我们有些学员干脆就没方向了：“提着”要怎么说啊？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个特点给我们的启发就是，当你想用英语来表达某件事的时候，最重要的就是先把这句话的主语和谓语（包括宾语）找出来，放在第一和第二的顺序把它们先说出来，然后再说其他的句子成分。有人问了，说完主语和谓语之后呢？后面的成分呢？这就是介词所担当的重任了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">说到这里，我们要对介词重新下个定义了，什么是介词？介词就是介绍句子中名词身份的词。从这个角度来说，我们把preposition这个词翻译成“介词”倒是非常恰当了。再说得具体一点，所谓的介词，就是：用于标明句子中除了主语和直接宾语外担任其他句子成分的名词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如前面的两个例句中，to school指的是目的地，by bike指的是方式，for work指的是目的地，school, bike, work在句子中都是名词，但却既不是主语，也不是宾语，所以需要分别用to, by, for三个介词来特别标明它们的身份。上面的其他例句也是如此，大家可以自己分析一下。下面再举一个典型的例子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">A bear walks from one end to the other end along a line under his owners order.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一只狗熊听从主人的命令沿着一条线从一端走到另一端。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话的内容非常丰富，一共出现了五个名词。除了主语bear之外，另外还有四个名词one end, the other end, a line和his owners order，分别说明了狗熊走前的位置、狗熊走后的位置、狗熊走的轨迹以及狗熊走的原因。如果我们按照汉语的思维方式来表达这句话，很可能会无所适从。因为汉语中光动词就有两个，“听从”和“走”，顺序也完全不一样。但英语中因为有了神奇的介词，问题就迎刃而解了，只要先把主语bear和谓语walk说完，其他的就用from, to, along和under四个介词分别说明就可以，甚至顺序打乱了也不会有很大的问题。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以，通过这些例句我们就能充分地领会到介词在理顺句子结构方面所起的巨大作用。它就像一个大管家，把一个句子收拾得井井有条，让我们的英语说得更省心。只要把主语和谓语找到先说出来，然后再用介词把其他的句子成分组织起来就可以了。当然，其他成分也不一定都是用介词结构表示的，也可能是副词、现在分词或者从句，但是毫无疑问，介词在其中占的比例是相当高的。至于如何用这些介词，在下面的章节中会讲到。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">不会用介词就不会说英语</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">介词意义重大，我们的学习者却不怎么会用介词。总结下来，主要存在以下三方面的问题：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">一、不会用介词表达抽象的词义</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">介词最初用于描述人或物的空间位置，但是，由于语言天生的比喻功能，介词经常会用来与抽象名词或人搭配表达抽象的概念，非常实用。如下面的这些例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">介词与抽象名词搭配</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">That's against the law.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">那是违法的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The evidence is against him.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">证据于他不利。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Were behind schedule.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们落后于进度了。〔还可以说ahead of schedule（比进度快），on schedule（正好卡在进度上）。〕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm under a lot of pressure lately.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我最近压力很大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The vaccine is against the flu.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个疫苗是用来防流感的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm in a hurry.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我有急事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You're in a big trouble.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你有大麻烦了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">介词与人搭配</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is under Louis.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他是路易斯的手下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Mathematics was always beyond me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">数学对我来说太难了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Its a secret between you and me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是你我之间的秘密。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm behind you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我支持你。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Dinner is on me tonight.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">今天的晚餐我请了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Wendy's in advertising.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">温迪从事广告行业。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">让介词成为你的左膀右臂</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">二、没有养成用介词的意识</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如前所述，介词在一个句子里面起着重要的理顺结构的作用，但因为受汉语思维的影响，大多数学员会在需要用到介词的时候却采用了其他的方式，就像前面举过的那些介词可以用来代替动词的情况，甚至一个从句的例子，我们多数人会在该用这些介词的时候用了动词或从句。再比如“用”这个词在我们的汉语中是会经常用到的，像下面的句子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们用树枝盖了个房子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个笔记本电脑用AA电池。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因为两句话里面有都有个“用”字，所以一般我们会习惯性地表达为：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We use branches to make a house.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The laptop uses AA batteries.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">实际上，下面的表达更符合英语的表达习惯：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We made a house with branches.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The laptop works on AA batteries.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上两句各用了一个介词代替汉语中的“用”，主要原因就在于我们没培养出英语的这种“动词+介词结构”的思维意识。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如何培养这种思维习惯呢？除了要练习在第一时间找到主语和谓语外，还要知道“介词结构”在句子中都可以扮演哪些角色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们知道，句子是用来描述一件事情的，除了主语和谓语分别说明了事情发生的主体和行为，一般还要说明以下四个方面的问题：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Why?事情发生的原因是什么？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">From where?从哪儿来？如“来源”“组成”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">To where?到哪儿去？如“方向”“目标”“目的”“结果”等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">How?怎么发生的？如“方式”“工具”等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">而“介词结构”也就是在句子中扮演以上四种角色。我们下面就给出例句来说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">表示原因</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He shouted out in pain.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他痛得大叫起来。（pain是大叫的“原因”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She felt sick from tiredness.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她累得病倒了。（tiredness是病的“原因”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I took her bag by mistake.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我不小心拿了她的包。（mistake是拿错包的“原因”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">表示来源、组成等</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He lives on water and leaves.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他靠喝水和吃树叶维持生命。（water和leaves是能活下去的“来源”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Steel is made from iron.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">钢是用铁炼成的。（iron是炼钢的材料）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This clothes is made of cotton.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这件衣服是用棉做的。（cotton是做衣服的材料）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">表示方向、目的、目标、结果等</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">She is working on her interview skills.</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她在练习她的面试技巧。（interview skill是练习的“目标”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He came to me for advice.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他来找我出主意。（me是come的“方向”，advice是come的“目的”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I shook my head in protest.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我摇头表示抗议。（protest是摇头的“目的”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She ripped the paper in two.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她把纸一撕两半。（two是撕的“结果”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">表示方式、工具等</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Roger spoke in a low voice.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Roger压低嗓音说话。（low voice是说话的“方式”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My I pay by cheque?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我能用支票付钱吗？（cheque是付钱的“工具”）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上例句大家在看的时候可以反思一下，你们也会用这些介词来表达吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，我们过去熟悉的很多句型也是这种“介词结构”的体现，比如我们经常说的：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm looking at her.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我正在看她。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">look后面的介词at就是用来说明look的方向。我们之所以没有感觉到它有什么特殊，是因为我们刚开始学英语的时候就把look at当成了一个固定搭配。其实，look后面还可以跟其他表示方向的介词，如look into, look through等，这些反倒是我们不大熟悉的了。再比如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Were talking in English.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们正用英语交流。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">talk后面跟的in是用来说明talk的方式的，我们对这种结构也非常熟悉了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">说到这里，大家现在应该充分理解“介词+名词”在句子中所起的这四个作用了吧？所以，以后我们在句子中需要表达这四个方面的内容时，都要有意识地考虑是否可以用“介词+名词”这种形式来代替。下面我就给大家出一些练习题，训练一下这方面的意识。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小试牛刀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以下句子中只有一个谓语动词，请找出来，并用“介词结构”表达其他部分的内容。为了降低难度，已给出了需要用到的介词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我的手被一片玻璃给划破了。（on）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">莉莉吃惊地看着我。（in）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她单脚站立。（on）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">价格上涨了10%。（by）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她正在吃从酒店带回来的食物。（from）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我去学校接妹妹。（from）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他的手冻僵了。（with）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">嘴里含着食物的时候不要说话。（with）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">让我们为你找到新工作喝一杯。（to）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">“下来”“过去”是介词不是动词</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">三、对off, over等重要介词的词义不了解</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这两个介词在口语中的用途非常广泛，但在实际的教学中，我们发现很多学员对这两个词的理解仅仅停留在“take off your clothes”和“game over”这样的固定搭配上，这是一个大大的不足。下面就分别讲解一下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">off</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">off的基本词义是“一物与另一物脱离”，这是最常见到的事物关系之一。但因为我们在汉语中没有与之对应的介词，只能表示为“下来”的意思，以至于我们的学习者对其无法留下深刻的印象。它主要有以下几个方面的用途：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">与具体事物搭配，表示一事物脱离另一事物</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Get your feet off my couch.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">把你的脚从我的沙发上拿开。（脚与沙发分离）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Why are all of the caps off the pens?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">为什么这些笔都没盖上盖？（盖子与笔分离）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I finally take his picture off the wall.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">最后我还是把他的照片从墙上摘了下来。（照片与墙脱离）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">James couldn't get the ring off his finger.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">詹姆斯没办法把戒指从手上取下来。（戒指与手指脱离）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The other driver forced my car off the road.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">另一个人开车把我的车挤出了道路。（车与道路脱离）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She was cleaning the blood off the floor.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她正在清洗地板上的血迹。（血迹与地板脱离）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">与抽象事物搭配，表示一个事物脱离某一状态</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She clears off a space next to her on the bed.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她在床上靠近她的地方清理出一块空地。（脱离原来杂乱的状态）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">This news has taken a load off my mind.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">听了这个好消息我就放心了。（心事没了）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He caught me off guard.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他搞得我猝不及防。（戒备心不在）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">over</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">over的基本词义是“从一个点到另一个点”，并可以延伸出一些抽象的词义来。汉语中经常表述为“过去”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">具体概念，“从一个地方到另一个地方”，或者“覆盖某一个地方”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Children went over the grass.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">孩子们跑过草地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Hand over the money！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">把钱递过来！（抢银行的时候）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'll send over some pie.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我会送些馅饼过去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I put another blanket over the baby.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我又给宝宝盖了层毯子。（我们经常会用on来代替）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There was broken glass all over the road.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">路上到处都是碎玻璃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">抽象概念，表示“胜过，超过，优于”等</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I've got over that relationship.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我已经从那段感情里走出来。（已战胜了失恋的痛苦）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm so over men.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我看透男人了。（我已超脱于对男人的依恋）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You want to break up with me over a suit?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">难道你会为了一件衣服和我分手？（感情还不如衣服重要）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You choose cigarettes over a guy?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你宁可与香烟为伴也不愿找男人？（男人还不如香烟）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">生活中有很多场合需要表达一件事情比另一件事情更重要，以上例句如果不用over这个带有意象功能的词的话，我们大多需要用prefer, important, care等词汇或比较级来代替。所以，以后再碰到类似场合的时候就要有意识地考虑一下是否可以用一个简单的“over”来代替、对比两者之间的地位或重要性。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">其他用法</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Id prefer to talk about it over the phone.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我更愿意在电话里谈。（工具，从电话的这一头到电话的那一头）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">One minute he's all over me, and the next he's pushing me away.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">刚刚还甜言蜜语，一会儿就对我置之不理了。（注意力，意思是心思全在她身上）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She told me one day over coffee.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有一天喝咖啡的时候她告诉我的。（场合，从开始喝咖啡到结束）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">介词的变身术</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与名词搭配在句子中担任重要角色只是介词重要性的一个体现，只能算是它的本职工作，作为英语的灵魂，介词的神奇之处还体现在它们可以根据句子的需要随时变身！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">介词变身为副词</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">首先，介词可以变身为副词与动词搭配，就是平时大家所说的动词短语。虽然大家对动词短语这个概念并不陌生，但用得却并不是很熟练。我们以off, out为例，它们就可以变身为副词和大多数的单纯动词搭配，一般表示动作的结果。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">off的基础词义是脱离，在短语中一般表示为“掉”“下来”等意思。如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She kicked off her shoes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她踢掉了鞋子。（kick是动作，off是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The hunter fought off two hungry tigers.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">猎人击退了两只饿虎。（fight是动作，off是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Let's run the fat off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">让我们把脂肪跑掉。（run是动作，off是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">All the witnesses were paid off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所有的证人都被收买了。（pay是动作，off是结果，结果就是所有的证人都不说话了。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Hes got a headache, he just slept it off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他头疼，睡一觉就好了。（sleep是动作，off是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I ate too much. I'll walk it off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我吃得太多了。我得走走消化消化。（walk是动作，off是结果。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">out的基础词义是“在外面”，表示“出来”“结束”等意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Add a little salt to bring out the flavor.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">加点盐把味道带出来。（bring是动作，out是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Lay out the map on the table.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">把地图在桌子上展开。（lay是动作，out是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm going to print my essay out.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我要把我的论文打印出来。（print是动作，out是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Blow all the candles out.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">把所有的蜡烛吹灭。（blow是动作，out是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The fire burns out.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">火烧尽了。（burn是动作，Out是结果）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，大多数的介词都可以变身为副词与单纯动词搭配。所以，我们就可以设置一些这样的搭配练习，让大家用这些搭配来造句，进一步熟悉这些单纯词的词义和介词的用法。以下是我们在培训时用到的例子，请大家尝试一下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">小试牛刀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请大家分别将左边的动词与右边一列的介词（副词）搭配，看能否组成一个合理的动词短语。如果可以，请用这个短语造个句子。最后查词典看看是否和你理解的一致。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">move/turn/look</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">down/up/in/out/on/off/over</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">介词变身为形容词</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">介词变身为副词的时候还需要有个动词与之搭配，所以，这时候的介词充其量只能算个配角。但当介词变身为形容词的时候那就不一样了，它既不需要颠颠地跑到名词前面去给人家介绍身份，也不需要跑到动词后面去看人脸色，迎合人家，这时候的它已蜕变为完完全全的主角了！这才真正体现了介词的超能量！请看下面的例句：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Do you know whats on tonight?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你知道今晚播什么节目吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The water is off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">停水了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The wedding is off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">婚礼取消了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The class is over.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下课了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You're never in when I call.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我每次打电话你都不在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Her flight is not in yet.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她的航班还没有到。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Long hair is in again.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">长头发又开始流行了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Don't you know tight jeans are out?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">难道你不知道紧身牛仔裤已经过时了吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Are the kids still up?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">孩子们还没睡吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Our computers are down right now.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们的电脑出故障了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">We have a party this weekend, so are you in or out?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们这周有个聚会，你参加吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">不知大家是否注意到，无论变身为形容词还是变身为副词，唱主角的都是那些表示动态位置的介词中表示“轨迹”的介词？主要原因就是这些词本身就说明了事物变化的轨迹，如in是“从外到里”，off是“从连接到脱离”，up是“从下往上”等，所以它们可以直接和动词搭配当副词，或者干脆把动词也抛开，自己独立表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\">\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h2 class=\"bodycontent-second-title\">英语的配角：副词及其他</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">副词</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">时间</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">now early just then recently ago already yet ever never forever</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">位置</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">here there</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">方向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">away forth apart together aside</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">数量</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000002982",
