            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">副词与连词、代词等在语言中都充当辅助的角色，在本书中不做重点讲解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">小结</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">到现在为止，1368个单词已经分门别类，有重点地介绍完了。是不是觉得收获很大？但同时也会觉得有点累，对不？信息量太大了！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面，我再对前面的内容做个简单的回顾，梳理一下，给你疲劳的大脑做个小小的按摩，让这1368个单词有一个清晰的脉络。主要从两个方面进行总结。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">词汇的用途</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们说一件事的时候，首先要知道我们说的是谁，知道名字的就说名字，不知道名字的就说它是哪一类的。说的是人还是物（具体名词），或者是事（抽象名词）。有时候，我们需要描述事物的某一个组成部分（构成类名词），或者它的某一个属性（属性类名词）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">确定是谁之后，我们一般会从两个角度来描述它，一是说它发生了什么，二是说它是什么样子的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">发生的事情也分两种，一种是它自己发生了什么变化（go或不及物动词），另一种是它让别的事物发生了什么变化（make something go或及物动词）。事物之间最常见的作用关系有三个（give, get, take），但有时候还需要说明得更具体：是谁让它发生的变化（原因），变化前是什么样的（来源），变化后是什么样的（方向、目标、目的、结果），是怎么发生变化的（方式）。这当中涉及事物之间关系的就用介词来表明，其他的该用副词用副词，该用形容词用形容词。我们可以用单纯动词与其他词搭配来表达，也可以用世故动词简洁地表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">描述事物的样子一般也分两种，要么是描述它们的组成，要么是描述它们的属性，都可以用“be+形容词”句式。形容词中又分为物的组成和属性，人的组成和属性，以及事的组成和属性，而物的组成和属性经常可以通过比喻的方法用到描述人与事的组成和属性上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">词汇的重要程度</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这1368个单词中，有些是只要我们背下来就可以的（具体名词），有些则需要掌握它们“以一顶百”的本领（大词）。每个类别中都有自己的核心词汇，一定要重点掌握，如构成类名词中的part和side，属性类名词中的size, way, point等。有些形容词非常形象，需要我们学会用它们表达抽象的事物。有一些词是我们汉语中没有对应词汇的，如形容词中的tough和rough，需要理解后重点掌握。介词最重要，但也是我们最不擅长使用的，是重点中的重点。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以，语言这东西虽然看上去千变万化，说穿了也就是那么一回事。把思路厘清了，我们学起来就轻松了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">二合一的学习方法</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有人可能会问，这些词汇确实非常重要，但我们只是学词汇吗？那些句型、语法什么的还要不要学呢？当然要学，只是学的方式不同。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们这本书主要讲了1368个单词的用法，表面看像是只在学单词，实际上我们是从整体上学英语这门语言，学单词的时候已包括了语法和句型知识。像我们前面在介绍这些词时就不只是介绍了它们的词义，还在不同的章节分别讲解了词汇的搭配、句型结构等语法内容：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">1.以policy和occasion为例讲了抽象名词与动词的搭配；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">2.以clean, clear为例讲了单纯型动词与介词的搭配，以“力量型”的单纯词为例讲了单纯型动词与副词、介词、名词的搭配；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">3.go与名词、介词、形容词搭配；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">4.及物动词与不及物动词的转换；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">5.名词向世故型动词的转换；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">6.介词与名词搭配所起到的中介作用；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">7.介词与抽象名词的搭配，与人的搭配；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">8.“主语+谓语+其他成分”的句型结构。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们是从事物的本质上，也就是事物的存在和发展规律上来分析为什么这些词可以搭配在一起，另外一些词则不能搭配，为什么要先说主语和谓语，然后再用介词结构，这样的学习比起孤立地看语法书更能给学习者留下深刻的印象。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以，我们在学这1368个单词的时候其实是同时学习了词义、短语和句型，是把词汇与语法结合起来的一种“二合一”的高效的学习方式，这是传统的英语教学所不具备的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">培养英语思维的有效途径</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家都知道，如果没有一个全英文的学习环境，培养英语思维是一件很难的事情。许多人说了多年的英语还是一口流利的Chinglish，主要原因就在于他们大多数时候还是在用中文进行思维。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">为什么英语思维的培养这么难呢？主要是受母语的影响与干扰，我们在学英语的时候总是会不自觉地借助汉语，而不是从要表达的事物本身来理解。所以，要想彻底摆脱母语的束缚，我们就必须超越语言本身直接研究事物的本质。这也正是我们在这本书里所做的工作。我们对这1368个单词都是从它们所反映的事物以及事物存在和发展的概念来理解的，而不只是简单地告诉大家它们的中文意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们的目的就是要通过对学习者的反复强化训练，让学习者在头脑中建立起事物的基本概念与英文的直接联系，这样就可以摆脱中文的束缚，真正培养起英语思维了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\">\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h2 class=\"bodycontent-second-title\">攻无不克的1368个单词</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">简单地回顾总结之后，也到了需要它们集体亮相、展示身手的时候了。就像奥运会一样，前面是入场式，现在是轮到它们在各个项目上协同作战、奋勇拼搏，夺取胜利的时候了。光说不练假把式，下面就用几个具体的场景来证明我们这1368个单词的超级能量。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">四个动词讲述一个餐厅里的故事</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是我们在课堂上的一个练习，是一个role play（角色扮演）。要求是：台词中除了系动词be外，其他地方需要用动词的地方全部用have, give, get, take这四个词来表达！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以下为汉语原文，你们可以自己先尝试一下：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一对男女朋友前去餐厅吃饭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：欢迎欢迎，有预订吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：没有。我们想要个靠窗的位子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：你们可以坐这个位子。想吃点什么？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：我可以看一下菜单吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：当然。给你。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：给我来份牛排，一杯果汁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：我要一个汉堡包，一杯咖啡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：可以拿走你们的菜单了吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：可以了。要多长时间？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：二十分钟吧！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：太慢了！我们很忙，给你十分钟时间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：好吧，我们试试。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">10分钟后。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：服务员呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：我去叫他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">（对服务员）：我们的菜呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：我马上就去拿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：这是你的牛排和果汁。这是你的汉堡和咖啡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">吃完饭后。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：埋单。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：可以刷卡吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：可以的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：不对呀！咖啡不是免费的吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：不是的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：你们牌子上写着：“买一送一”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：没有啊！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：少给我来这套！把你老板叫来！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：要不这样吧！我们免费送你一个冰激凌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：好吧！再帮我们叫辆出租车。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：好的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以下为参考译文：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一对男女朋友前去餐厅吃饭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：欢迎欢迎，有预订吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Welcome. Do you have a reservation?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：没有。我们想要个靠窗的位子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">No. Wed like to have a table by the window.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：你们可以坐这个位子。想吃点什么？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You can take this one. What would you like to have?/What can I get for you?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：我可以看一下菜单吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">May I have the menu?/Could you give me the menu?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：当然。给你。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Of course. Here you are.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：给我来份牛排，一杯果汁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'll have a steak, a glass of juice.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：我要一个汉堡包，一杯咖啡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Id like to have a hamburger, a cup of coffee.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：可以拿走你们的菜单了吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">May I take the menu?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：可以了。要多长时间？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Please. How long will it take?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：二十分钟吧！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">About twenty minutes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：太慢了！我们很忙，给你十分钟时间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">That's too long. We’re busy.Well give you ten minutes./Youonly have ten minutes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：好吧，我们试试。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Ok. Well give it a try.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">10分钟后。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：服务员呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Where is the waiter?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：我去叫他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'll get him.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">（对服务员）：我们的菜呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Where are our dishes?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：我马上就去拿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'll take them right now.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：这是你的牛排和果汁。这是你的汉堡和咖啡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Here is your steak and Juice. Here is your hamburger and coffee.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">吃完饭后。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：埋单。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">May I have the bill, please?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：可以刷卡吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Do you take credit card?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：可以的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Sure.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：不对呀！咖啡不是免费的吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Something is wrong！Isnt the coffee free?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：不是的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Sorry, no.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：你们牌子上写着，“买一送一”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There is a note on your sign，“buy one, get one for free.”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：不是的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Not really.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">女：少给我来这套！把你老板叫来！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Don't give me that！Get your boss here！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：要不这样吧！我们免费送你一个冰激凌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">How about this?Well give you an ice cream for free.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">男：好吧！再帮我们叫辆出租车。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">All right. Then get a taxi for us.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">服务员：好的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">OK.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">怎么样？是否感觉不可思议？什么找位子、点菜、上菜、刷卡、吵架统统可以用have, give, get, take来表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">当然在实际生活中，我们的表达可能会更丰富一些，这个练习只是为了让学员体会到这四个词的巨大作用，加深他们对使用这些词的印象。这是一种强化训练。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">只用介词解说一场足球比赛</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这也是我们课堂中的一个练习。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">看到标题，你可能会觉得有些夸张吧？当然，需要说明的是，我们这儿所说的解说并不是像真正的解说员那样专业，而只是为了让你在看足球比赛的时候能把比赛中的一些关键点表述出来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们先来看看足球比赛中最常表达的东西都有哪些：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他上场了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他下场了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他上场替下了队友。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球出了边线。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球打正了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球打偏了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">边裁举旗了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球打到了队友身上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">比赛进入了伤停补时阶段。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">主队1:0领先。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们对学员提出了两个要求，首先，全部用介词表述以上内容，而且只能用be，不能用其他动词。主要是为了强化大家对介词使用的意识，不要受动词的影响。以下为参考答案：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他上场了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is on.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他下场了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他上场替下了队友。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He is on for his teammate.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球出了边线。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The ball is over the line.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球打正了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The shot is on the goal.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球打偏了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The shot is off the goal.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">边裁举旗了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The flag is up.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">球打到了队友身上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The ball is onto his teammate.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">比赛进入了伤停补时阶段。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The game is into the injury time.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">主队1:0领先。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The home team is 1:0 ahead.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">然后要求学员主要用上面的表达来解说一场足球比赛，这一次可以在介词前面添加一些具体的动词，如go, take, kick, pass, shoot, hit等。这样的话就可以把动词和介词放在一起进行强化练习，在这里就不给参考答案了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">为“大话西游”配台词</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">电影《大话西游之仙履奇缘》中孙悟空对紫霞仙子说的那一段经典爱情表白大家都耳熟能详了。这段独白看上去不是很简单，如果让大家用英语来表达会存在一些困难，我们先来看一下这段台词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">曾经，有一份真诚的爱情放在我面前，我没有珍惜，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">等到我失去的时候才后悔莫及，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">人世间最痛苦的事莫过于此……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果上天能够给我一个再来一次的机会，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我会对那个女孩子说三个字：“我爱你。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果非要在这份爱上加上一个期限，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我希望是……一万年！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">里面有几个语言点大家会比较纠结，“真诚”要怎么说？多数人会用sincere，“珍惜”会说成cherish，“后悔”会用regret，“痛苦”很多人则不知道怎么说。最难的是“期限”，有用period的，有用limit的，最不靠谱是用deadline的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其实，这些看上去比较难的表达，都可以用我们R词汇表中最简单的、连初中生都能看得懂的词来表达。请看参考译文：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I ever had a true love. I didn't take it.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm very sorry after I lost it.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is the worst thing in the world.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">If the God could give me one more chance，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I would tell the girl，“I love you.”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">If you ask me how long I want it to be，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I hope it could be 10，000 years！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">简单吧？很简单，读起来还非常顺畅。最后这个词“期限”我们甚至没有用一个专门的名词，但照样把意思说得非常清楚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">讲述社会新闻</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是我们在课堂上经常用到的训练方式。老师会从门户网站随机抽取一些新近发生的社会新闻，让学员用自己所掌握的词汇进行描述。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个练习的难点在于，社会新闻是一种比较正式的文体，所以里面会有很多书面的表达。学员要快速地转变自己的思维，用我们在词汇表中学过的大词、形象词以及单纯词来进行表达。请看下面一个例子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">去年11月，徐州一所中学的一名就读学生被学校勒令退学。原因是这名学生在教室内与女同学接吻，被摄像头记录了下来。学生的家长认为校方的处分过重，和学校进行过多次沟通。但是校方称，在教室内公然接吻，给同学们带来极坏的影响，这是严重违反校规的，属于可以予以勒令退学的情况。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上表达中有几个难点：“勒令退学”“记录”“处分过重”“沟通”“违反”等，都是比较正式的官方语言。我们来看看参考译文：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Last November, a middle school student in XuZhou was kicked out because he kissed a girl in the classroom. A video camera caught it.His parents thought the punishment was too heavy.They talked with the school for some times.The school said, it had a bad effect on other students to kiss in the classroom.It was against the school rules badly.So he must leave the school.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">“勒令退学”用的是动词短语kick out，“记录”用的是单纯动词catch，“处分过重”用的是形象词heavy，“沟通”用的是单纯动词talk，“违反”用的是介词against。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">虽然用词很简单，但整个事件却描述得非常清楚，非常符合英语的口语化表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">描述工作经历</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">或许有的读者还会担心这1368个单词在工作中是否用得上，那就请大家看看下面这个案例，这是在面试的时候回答关于自己做过的工作，先看看中文要表达的内容：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我的第一份工作是在Radio Shack（无线电器材公司）做一名销售员。通过这份工作我学会了如何与客户打交道，我的独立性更强了。我很喜欢那份工作，但我觉得应该多锻炼一下自己。于是，我就辞职，在Verizon（威瑞森电信）找了一个新的职位。我在那儿做行政，杂七杂八的事很多，比如做计划、做报表，以及安排一些会议。这份工作让我学到了一些东西但我还是想做销售。所以我就抓住了一个机会，在Verizon的一个店铺里卖手机。我充分发挥了以前积累的销售经验，工作也很卖力。连续三年，我都被评为最佳销售员。我在那里一直工作到现在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因为面试是一种严肃的场合，所以我们的回答会比较正式一些。以上描述中有几个比较难的语言点：“打交道”“独立性”“锻炼”“行政”“报表”“安排”“发挥”等。我们来看看参考译文：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My first job was working at Radio Shack as a salesman. I learned a lot how to work with customers, and I could do a lot of things on my own.I enjoyed my work there, but I wanted to experience more.So I left it and got a new position in Verizon.It was an office job.I had different tasks, such as planning, doing some paperwork, and fixing meetings.I learned some but I wanted to get back into sales.So I was given an opportunity to sell mobile phones for Verizon at a store.I used my past sales experience and worked hard.I became one of the top sales for three years.I've been there ever since.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">“打交道”用的是单纯词work with，“独立性”用的是介词结构on ones own，“锻炼”用的是experience，“行政”用的是office job，“报表”用的是paperwork，“安排”用的是单纯词fix，“发挥”用的是单纯词use。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这些表达不但流畅，而且完全可以被面试官所接受，不会让对方感觉不正式。对学习者来说，最重要的是能不能清楚地表达，而不是非要追求和老外说得一样地道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">1368个单词是学好英语的突破口</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上五个实例描述了五个不同的场景，分别涵盖了生活、体育、电影、社会新闻、求职面试，充分地说明了我们这个R词汇表是完全可以解决生活、工作中大部分沟通交流的问题的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有人会问，现在我知道这1368个单词用于口语表达足够了，但阅读怎么办？听力怎么办？写文章或者说话不可能只用这1368个单词吧，这就是另外一个问题了。毫无疑问，对听说读写四种技能的任何一种来说，词汇量大都是一种优势，但是，我们首先要考虑的是找到一个突破口，让你的英语能够尽快用起来的突破口。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">打个比方，有这么两个人，一个口语好，但词汇量不大，所以听力会相对差一些，另一个词汇量很大，老外说的大部分都能听懂，但自己说不出来，你认为老外会更乐意和谁交流？一定是前者，因为你听不懂的地方对方还可以给你解释，但如果你有话说不出来，就算你听得懂，谈话也会很快结束。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以说先用这1368个单词让自己能够表达，是学好英语的一个重要的突破口。会说了，就有自信了，也就有了成就感，然后就可以通过在工作和生活的实际运用中快速地提升英语能力了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\">\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h1 class=\"bodycontent-first-title\">下篇　如何掌握这1368个单词？</h1></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">好了，说到这儿，这1368个单词都是谁，它们都有什么本领我们已经介绍得清清楚楚了。我相信很多读者已经迫不及待地想把这1368个单词学到手了。那要怎么学呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">任何语言的学习都离不开两个重要的环节，一个是input，一个是output，专业地讲叫“输入”和“输出”，通俗地说就是“学”和“练”。先要学到东西，才能有东西可练，大家对这个观点应该没什么异议吧？好的，那下面我们就从“学”和“练”两个阶段来看看要如何把这神奇的1368个单词变成自己的东西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\">\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h2 class=\"bodycontent-second-title\">怎么学？</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">首先是顺序问题。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">1368个单词虽然不多，但在年龄上却是有长幼的，地位上是有尊卑的，我们必须根据它们的内在关系排出先后顺序才能省时省力地把它们学到手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">先大词后小词</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">前面大家已经了解了，所谓“大词”就是指那些用处特别多的词，具体可以理解为名词中的类别词、构成词，动词中的单纯词，以及形容词中描述物的词等，也可以理解为我们所说的上义词，即可以代替很多其他词的词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">道理我想就不用多讲了，就像我们吃葡萄时总会先拣大的吃一样，学英语我们总会先拣最给力的学。这样安排是出于以下三个方面的考虑：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一是这些词的用途非常广泛，大多都有一个顶一百个的本领。先学会它们更快速地解决我们的表达问题。如big, get, way这些词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">二是它们都是身体可以直接感知的词，与抽象词汇比较起来更容易理解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如rough与general相比，size与importance相比，put together与assemble相比。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">三是这些词的很多词义和用法在我们之前的学习中是被严重忽视的，所以才要先拾起来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">像名词中的side, end，动词中的go, make等，形容词中的heavy, sharp等，介词中的off, over等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">先中式后英式</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话并不是说要教大家说中式英语，而是说大家要先学习与中式思维比较接近的词汇、搭配和句型，然后再逐渐过渡到典型的英语思维。道理也很简单，因为大家已经熟悉了汉语的思维模式，想要转换到另一种差别较大的思维模式必须从易到难，有一个循序渐进的过程。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">确切地讲，这个过程可以分成三个阶段：中式思维阶段，简单英语思维阶段，典型英语思维阶段。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">什么是中式思维，什么又是典型的英语思维呢？我通过一些例子来说明两者之间的递进关系吧！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">比如有这么一句话：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这场车祸导致了10人死亡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话可以有三种不同的表达，分别是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The car accident caused 10 people die.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The car accident killed 10 people.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The car accident claimed 10 lives.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">第一句基本是汉语表达的翻版，无论是在用词上还是语序上。第二句是英语中口语化的表达，用了kill这个词。第三句是英语中比较正式的表达，用了claim这个词。需要先说明的一点是，这三种表达都没有任何问题，都是可以被接受的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">很显然，我们的初学者是很容易接受第一种表达方式的，因为这一句不需要我们做什么思维转换，只要把这些词掌握了就可以。第二句需要对自己的思维做个调整，把一个“cause+直接宾语+补足语”的句型变成一个“动词+直接宾语”的句型，但因为用的是kill这个大家比较熟悉的口语词汇，所以这个转换并不是很难。但第三句就是大家最不容易掌握的了，因为无论是在句型结构上还是用词上都与汉语的表达有很大的差别。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这三句话基本上代表了我们的学员所要经历的三个思维阶段。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">在实际的教学中，我们首先会鼓励学员用第一种方式来表达，因为根据前面动词的介绍，make是一个与be, go一样的本源词，掌握了它的用法可以解决学员的很多表达问题。但同时会提醒学员有一个词就是“make somebody die”的意思，让他们主动记起用kill这个词，这样不但教会了他们kill在这句话里的用法，而且进一步强化了他们把“makesomething/somebody do something”的单纯词句型往世故词句型转化的意识。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如进一步教他们下面这些世故词的类似用法：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">make somebody angry=annoy</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">make somebody happy=entertain</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">make something work=operate</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">前面的那个例子中，最后一句claim的用法则是在培训的提升阶段，等到大家已经比较熟悉了世故词的用法之后，再进一步教他们更加正式的表达方式。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上是“单纯动词”往“世故动词”思维的转换，但更多时候是需要帮助学员从“世故动词”往“单纯动词”思维转换。如学员在用reduce的时候我们要提醒他们可以用cut down来代替，用return的时候可以用give back来代替。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其次是输入的方式。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">看过《英语思维是这样炼成的》的读者都知道，我在书中提倡通过体验来学习英语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">其实这并非是我提倡或不提倡的事情，这本来就是语言学习的必由之路。只是因为我们不具备充足的语言环境，就不得不采取书本教学这种比较机械的方式。但实际上，我们依然能够在现实生活中创造出一些方法增加体验感。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">什么叫体验式学习？简单来说，就是边演示边学。有画面，有声音，学习者能够参与其中。你必须让语言所表达的内容在实际生活中能直接运用，这样才能理解透彻，记得牢。根据这几年积累的教学经验，我把几种比较有效的输入方式向大家介绍一下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">现场演示</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因为我们这1368个单词是以可感知的形象词汇为主，这让我们的体验式教学成为可能。下面通过几个案例来说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例一　吃牛蹄筋</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学内容：形容词tough</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学道具：牛蹄筋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">tough是词表中一个比较重要的形容词，有六个非常实用的词义，分别例示如下：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">1.艰难的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It was a tough decision to make.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是一个艰难的决定。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">2.强硬的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Hes getting tough with me.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他开始变得强硬起来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">3.强势的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">She is a tough business woman.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">她是个商界女强人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">4.粗暴的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">He plays the tough guy in the movie.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他在电影中演坏蛋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">5.咬不动的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The beef is tough.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">牛肉咬不动。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">6.坚硬的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The crocodiles skin is tough.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">鳄鱼皮很硬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上六个词义个个都很实用，既可以用在生活上，也可以用在工作中。这个词虽然和hard, strong的词义比较相近，但两者都无法替代这个词，因为它的六个词义都还含有“难以对付”的意思。所以，掌握这个词还是非常有必要的。要怎么掌握呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">经过比较可以看出，六个词义中的第五个“咬不动的”这个词义是最形象、最容易被感知的，所以，如果能让大家亲身体会到“咬不动”的感觉，就会更容易掌握这个词。而食物当中牛蹄筋是最有代表性的了，所以，在学这个词之前会让每个学员先吃一块牛蹄筋（没煮透的最好），问问他们感觉如何，知不知道这种感觉要用哪一个英语单词来形容最合适，最后再把今天要学的tough这个词告诉他们。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这种输入方式会给学员留下非常深刻的印象，因为他们是亲口品尝过的，比起我们只是口头告诉他们“牛蹄筋是tough的”印象要深得多。在此基础上再引导他们回忆还有哪些食品或东西有tough的感觉的，再进一步引导什么样的人会给他们tough的感觉，一步一步就可以把tough的几个词义一次性地搞懂、记牢。最后还可以把它的反义词tender引导进来一起学习。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例二　分香烟</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学内容：动词offer</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学道具：香烟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">学员对offer这个词的理解大部分停留在求职的时候应聘单位发给他们的offer上，这儿是当名词用。但实际上offer在当动词用的时候用处更多。词典中对这个词的解释是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">to say you are willing to do something for somebody or give something to somebody.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">意思是“说你乐意为别人做什么事情或把东西给别人”。这种表达在生活和工作中是经常见到的，但因为汉语中我们没有一个与之对应的词，所以学员就不会想到用这个词，或者用give来替代。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">老师会拿一盒香烟递给每一位学员，然后问他们抽不抽，这样一圈下来后就开始让他们用英语表达老师刚才的这个动作。根据我们的经验，大多数学员会说成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My teacher gave me a cigarette.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这时老师就要告诉他们：错了。然后再重新拿起这盒烟，从中抽出一根直接放到学员的面前桌子上，告诉他们，这才是give！而刚才的那个行为叫offer，正确的表达应该是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">My teacher offered me a cigarette.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">通过这种演示，就可以让学员清楚地理解offer和give的区别，印象会非常深。在此基础上再通过启发将这个词的用法进一步延伸到offer“职位”上、Offer“服务”上、offer“价钱”上、offer“回报”上等等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例三　拉绳子</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学内容：名词　line, end</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">动词　run, pass</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">形容词　tight, loose</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学道具：一根绳子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 1　问大家绳子要怎么说，除了rope外也可以用它的上义词line来表达。然后启发大家绳子的两头就是end。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 2　在教室里找两个柱状的物体，如门的把手或椅子腿，并边演示边启发大家如何表达：Run a rope between a chair and a door.（在椅子和门之间拉一根绳子。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 3　捆绑绳子的时候要多绕几圈，一边绕一边告诉大家可以用pass来表达：Pass the rope around the handle three times.（绳子绕门把手三圈。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 4　把绳子拉紧或放松，告诉大家分别可以用tight和loose这两个形容词来表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 5　让学员亲自动手做一遍，边做边用英语表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 6　再进一步讲解以上这些词的抽象用法，如a tight budget（预算很紧），a tight schedule（行程很紧），a loose group（松散的团体）等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，在演示的过程中，可以进一步延伸出更多的学习内容和更多的实用表达，这个需要老师根据现场情况灵活发挥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">看视频</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">受现场条件所限，毕竟不是所有的教学内容都可以进行课堂演示的，尤其是在网络教学越来越受欢迎的情况下，所以就需要有更多的选择。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">视频教学以及下面将要提到的图片教学、口语化教学都是在课堂现场演示无法实现的情况下采取的一种退而求其次的教学方式。虽然体验性比前者差一些，但依然比传统的课堂文字教学要强很多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例四　观钱塘江潮</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学内容：形容词awesome</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学道具：视频“钱塘江潮”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">awesome这个词在口语中用途很广泛，但却很难用一个词来概括它的含义，既可以表达“令人畏惧的”，也可以表达“惊人的”，还可以表达“很棒的”，每一种表达都没有办法让学员准确地明白这个词到底说的是什么意思，所以必须通过亲身体验才能让他们真正了解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">“钱塘江潮”的壮观景象是最适合用这个词来形容的，当然我们没办法直接把学员拉到钱塘江口现场体验，但可以通过放视频录像的方式让他们体会到那种awesome的感觉，很壮观，又有点吓人。再进一步引导到对“美丽景色”的形容，对“艰巨任务”的形容等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例五　挤地铁</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学内容：动词　push, fit, move</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">名词　way</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">介词　on, off, in</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">名词　space</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学道具：高峰时间乘客挤地铁的视频，有人下车，有人上车</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">播放视频，并同时告诉大家“挤”可以用push来表达。“有人挤着上车，有人挤着下车”可以表达为：Some people are pushing their way on.Some people are pushing their way off.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">“车厢里挤不下更多的人”可以用fit表达为：There's no space for more people to fit in.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">挤地铁是上班族每天都要经历的事情，所以，即使不是在现场，大家也可以“轻松”感受到这些词的真实含义，那都是血和泪啊！更大的意义在于，学员下次挤地铁的时候可能就会自然而然地想起在课堂上学到的这些内容，输入和输出两个环节这么一结合，“金风玉露一相逢，便胜却人间无数”，就一辈子忘不了了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">用图片</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这在我们研发的教学PPT里是用得最多、最喜闻乐见的一种教学手段，因为图片好找嘛！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例六　喝酸奶，吃光面</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学内容：形容词plain</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学道具：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><div class=\"tupian\"><$image alt=\"\" class=\"image-alone\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/images/images/00001.jpeg\"></$image></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><div class=\"tupian\"><$image alt=\"\" class=\"image-alone\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/images/images/00002.jpeg\"></$image></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">两张图片看得很清楚吧？一碗面和一杯酸奶，不过，这面可不是普通的面，是碗“光面”，就是没加任何浇头的面（有的地方也叫阳春面，诗意多了）。这酸奶也不是普通的奶，是“原味”酸奶，就是没加任何其他风味的酸奶。这两样东西都是大家在生活中非常熟悉的，所以，当学员知道这两样东西都可以用plain来形容的时候，大家自然就能明白plain这个词的真实含义了——指不加任何修饰或装饰的东西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">延伸开来，那以下表达分别是什么意思呢？不用我讲了吧！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">plain dress, plain house, plain speaking……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例七　杀鱼</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学内容：动词clean</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学道具：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><div class=\"tupian\"><$image alt=\"\" class=\"image-alone\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/images/images/00003.jpeg\"></$image></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">教学说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">图片中这人在干吗呢？没错，在收拾鱼。把鱼杀死之后，正在开膛破肚，把里面的肠子、鱼膘、苦胆啥的统统清理掉。这在英语中就表述为clean the fish, clean一个词就解决问题。当然，延伸开来，我们还会clean the chicken。不过，在杀鸡这个事情上，我们的观念就和老外不大一样了，当我们在clean the chicken的时候，其实并不是把里面的东西都扔掉了，像鸡心、鸡胗啥的都会留着，对我们来说这是美味，而不是要clean的东西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">学了这个用法之后，我们就可以延伸到其他东西上了。鱼可以clean，鸡可以clean，意思是把无用的或有害的东西统统处理掉，那在一个机构里面，如政府或公司里面，也同样存在着一些无用或者有害的人。比如，销售队伍中可能就会存在一些拿回扣的害群之马，那么我们可以用这个词表达为clean the sales team。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">有人可能会说了，像什么“阳春面”啊，“酸奶”啊，“杀鱼”什么的，这些我们都很熟悉啊，为什么一定要找张图片来给我们看呢？我们又不是小孩学看图识字。哎，你可别说，学汉语可能不需要把你当小孩子，但在学外语这事上，还真得把大家当小孩子来看待。这和语言的输入规律有关，形象记忆永远比文字记得深刻。只有给你最形象的图片或视频，你才能记忆深刻。就拿那张杀鱼的图片来说，今天你看过了，过段时间如果你自己杀鱼或看到别人杀鱼的时候，你一定会条件反射似的想到clean这个词，赌不？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">另外，我们的教学课件中所选用的无论是图片或视频，一定是中国人最熟悉的场景，比如讲plain food的时候，我们会选大家都熟悉的“阳春面”而不是“比萨”，因为阳春面我们经常见，一看到图片脑子里马上就能想起那种热腾腾的感觉，那种鲜美的味道，甚至是用筷子吃到嘴里那种呼噜呼噜的声音，这些东西都有助于加强你的理解和记忆。就像咱们了不起的诺贝尔奖获得者、我的老乡莫言所说的，写出来的东西一定要让大家都能看到画面甚至听到声音。这就是他写小说能得奖的重要原因，也是我们的教学效果更好的原因，嘿嘿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">口语化的翻译</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果我们学的某一个词或某一个表达是抽象的东西，既无法现场演示也无法用视频或图片进行可视化的表达，那我们还有最后一招，就是把它用汉语进行口语化的理解。道理和前面是一样的，目的就是为了加强体验感。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">举例来说，end up这个短语很有用，意思是“以什么样的结果收场”，如果我们只是用英文原版教材或词典中的例句，比如其中有一句是这样的：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Whenever I go out to dinner with them, I always end up paying the bill.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">只要我跟他们一起出去吃饭，最后总是我付账。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">那么学习者的印象并不会很深刻，只是理解而已。但如果把例句换成下面这样的：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The guys who win the fights over their girlfriends all end up single.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">看懂了吗？这句话的意思是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">跟女朋友吵架能赢的，最后都单身了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">印象深了吗？一定很深。因为这句话是一句网络流行语，无论是“00后”，还是“90后”、“80后”都很熟悉。因为你熟悉，所以你会记住end up这个词的用法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">即使我们找不到像上面这样经典的例句，我们也有办法解决这个问题。比如前面那个例句，大家印象不深的重要原因不在于大家对“吃饭掏钱”这个场景不熟悉，而是它的中文翻译不够到位。如果我们这句话换一种说法，说成：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">每次和他们下馆子，掏钱的都是我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">是不是一下子感觉“高大上”了很多，形象了很多？因为这才是生活中我们常说的语言，前面那个一板一眼的翻译我们能理解，但生活中很少会这么说。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">再举个例子，aggressive这个词在不同的语境中会有不同的理解，并没有一成不变的词义。比如下面这句话：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You sound pretty aggressive！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果按词典里的解释，就会把它翻译成“你听上去很有侵略性”，“你听上去咄咄逼人”或者“你听上去是在挑衅”，虽然有那么点意思，但都不是我们生活中通常会说的，但如果你把它翻译成“你说话怎么这么冲！”一下子就境界全出了。下次如果有人对你说话很冲的时候，你很快就可以想到用aggressive了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个事的原理在于，在我们还没有办法完全达到用英语思维的情况下（事实上这是很难的，即使像我这样专门研究英语思维的人也时不时地会碰到汉语来搅局，而那些在国外浸淫多年的海归，也同样会受到汉语的影响），汉语经常会第一个跑到我们的头脑中，那我们要做的就是尽量在第一时间内把它用熟悉的英语表达出来。如果我们在“输入”这个环节就已经把地道的英语和地道的汉语做了一个直接的对接，那么我们在用英语表达的时候就可以借助口语化的汉语最快速地找到对应的英语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以，按照我的评判标准，一个好的英语老师不应该仅仅是英语说得溜就行的，在汉语方面也要有深入浅出的能力，看到一句英语能很快地反应过来在汉语中通常是如何表达的，这样才能最大限度地帮助学员掌握和理解所学的内容。所以，按这样的标准，在国内，最优秀的英语老师不应该是只会讲英语的所谓English native speaker，他们可以做一个很好的输出陪练对象，但谈到“教英语”，最好的老师一定是英语汉语俱佳的Chinese native speaker。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\">\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h2 class=\"bodycontent-second-title\">怎么练？</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">谈完了输入就该谈输出了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如前所述，输入是“学”，输出就是“练”。我们学的是这1368个单词，练的也是这1368个单词。有人可能会觉得，既然这些词都已经学过了，也都知道是什么词义了，张开嘴说不就完了吗？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">没那么简单。与输入一样，输出也要讲究顺序和方式。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">输出顺序</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">输出练习的顺序和语言的组成结构一致。语言最小的构成单位是单词，其次是词组，也就是短语之类的东西，然后再由这些词或词组构成一个个句子，句子再一个个连成段落。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">英语的输出练习也是这样，我们要先从最基本的单词开始练起，然后进行搭配练习，再练句子，最后再做段落或对话练习。这样做的目的有两个：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一是降低学习的难度。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">让学习者从难度最低的练习开始，逐渐过渡到难度大的表达，使大家有一个逐渐适应、循序渐进的过程。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">二是这种做法符合语言学习的基本规律。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们认为，单词是英语这门语言的基本单位，掌握了词或词组才是掌握句子的前提和基础，这是必须要先解决的问题。我们经常会碰到这样的情况，一个语法好的英语学习者如果用错了词，对方会听得一头雾水。而一个英语水平差的人，哪怕只用一个词，也能让对方听懂。北京的秀水街、上海以前襄阳路上的小商贩与老外讨价还价都是用这种蹩脚但实用的英语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这种做法与传统的英语教学有所不同。传统的英语教学无论是在输入还是在输出上，都是以一个对话或一篇文章为单位进行的，只是就其中的生词或句型进行另外的讲解。这种做法虽然可以让学习者尽快地掌握一些固定的表达方式（很多人是死记硬背），但因为他们并没有完全理解构成这些句子的单词或词组真正的含义或用法，以至于离开这些句子之后就没有办法灵活表达了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面的章节中我们所讲的输出练习方式基本都是按照这个顺序来的，只是略有侧重。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\"><span class=\"jiacu\">输出方式</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与输入一样，我们所设计的输出练习也特别强调了体验性。主要有以下几种。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">看视频</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例八　摊煎饼果子</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">训练内容：动词　spread, crack, fold, put, turn, heat</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">介词　over, off</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">名词　side</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">道具：一段做煎饼果子的视频</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">煎饼果子是一种天南地北中国人最喜欢吃的早餐，用它来做教学材料最能加强学员的体验感。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 1　播放视频</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">做煎饼果子主要有以下几个步骤：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">1.把面糊摊在平底锅上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">2.打一个鸡蛋在煎饼上并摊开。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">3.把煎饼翻过来加热。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">4.用刷子抹上酱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">5.放上脆饼或油条。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">6.把饼对折。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 2　请学员用英语讲解煎饼果子的制作过程。不对语法和句子的长短做固定要求，只要学员能够用到上面提到的几个关键词，甚至只是说出这几个词都可以。如下面的表达：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">摊面糊　spread it</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">打鸡蛋　crack an egg</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">揭下来　take it off</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">翻面　turn it over</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">对折　fold it</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一面加热　heat one side</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">如果学员能够顺利地想到上面这几个词，那么说明这个学员已对这几个词有充分的理解了。如果没有，老师可以启发他们回忆之前学到的内容。关键在于，一旦学员能够主动地用上一次，那么他就永远不会忘记这个词的使用方法了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，这个练习可以根据学员的level分好几个阶段进行重复练习。最初只是词或短语，然后要求学员说完整的句子，最后要求学员进行生动形象的大段描述。这对老师的英语水平和现场发挥都会提出很高的要求。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例九　《杜拉拉升职记》</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">训练内容：略</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">道具：电视剧《杜拉拉升职记》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">看国产电影或电视剧是我们独创的另外一个口语训练模式。前面说过，在国内学英语，口语的好坏主要看学习者在英语和汉语之间的快速转换能力，而优秀的国产电影或电视剧就提供了这样的机会。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">好的电影或电视剧的特点之一是它们的台词都比较生活化，用的都是我们平时经常说的语言。以它们作为训练目标有助于在学习者的头脑中建立起地道口语和地道英语之间的直接对接。我们选择《杜拉拉升职记》不仅仅是因为剧中口语化的语言，另一个原因是这部关于职场的电视剧，可以训练学习者在外企的口语能力。下面就拿剧中的一些典型台词来说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">台词一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">陪我喝一杯？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话的场景是，男主角去酒吧，碰到一个认识的女性朋友正在独自一人喝酒。她就邀请男主角一起喝酒，说了这么一句话。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话非常口语化，也比较容易误导学习者说成：Would you like to drink with me together?其实这句话主要训练学员对join这个词的掌握，比较地道的说法应该是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Join me?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">大家在美剧中可能经常会看到这样的表达，但回到现实生活中却往往不能马上反应过来。这就是我们需要做这种转换练习的意义。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">台词二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">要不然他以后会更嚣张！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话的场景是，HR经理让市场部经理参加展会，市场部经理借口不去。HR经理觉得太过分了，决定给他一个教训，然后就说了这么一句话。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">嗯，这就是office politics（办公室政治），我们在工作中经常碰到的，两个部门之间掐架。很多学员看到这句话的第一反应是去找一个对应的形容词，其实它是用来训练大家对go这个词的掌握能力的，我们给出的参考答案是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Or hell go even further.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">台词三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">时限是两分钟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话的场景是，杜拉拉去外企应聘，面试官给她出了道题，让她把一块蛋糕分给几个人，并限定了时间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话主要训练学员对句子主语的转换能力，当然你可以把句子直译为：The time limit is two minutes.但不够口语化，比较地道的说法应该是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You only have two minutes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">台词四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">他是不是跟市场部有仇啊？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这句话说的同样是办公室政治。杜拉拉刚入职，销售部经理看她是新手就刁难她，她不明就里，就跟前台小姑娘说了这样一句话。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这在汉语中也是很口语化的说法，你在英语当中很难查到“仇”这个词。其实我们也是在训练学员对口语表达的快速转换能力，我们提供的参考答案是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Does he have any problems with our department?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">搭配练习</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">搭配是我们在掌握了词汇的含义之后第二步要做的事情。最需要掌握的搭配模式主要有两种：名词和动词的搭配，动词和介词的搭配。下面就各举一例说明一下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例十　来一次轰轰烈烈的感冒</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">训练内容：名词cold与动词的搭配练习</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们的学员在输入环节已经学到与cold有关的表达方式，这个练习就是让学员能对所有这些学过的表达进行一些汇总、总结。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 1</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与have, give, get三个词的搭配，分别表达为：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I have a cold.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我感冒了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">You gave me the cold.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">你把感冒传染给了我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I got the cold from you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我的感冒是你传染的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 2</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与go的搭配，表达为：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The cold just doesn't go away.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">感冒老是好不了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 3</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与catch, spread, come down, shake off, pass on的搭配，表达为：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I caught a cold.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我感冒了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The cold spreads easily.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个感冒很容易传染。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I'm coming down with a cold.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我感冒了，很难受。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I cant seem to shake off the cold.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我感冒就是好不了了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">I don't want to pass on the cold to you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我不想把感冒传染给你。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上三个步骤的练习是由易到难逐级递进的，越往后的表达越形象生动。这些词并不要求大家都掌握，主要是通过反复练习培养以下几个方面的能力：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">摆脱汉语的影响，第一时间找到这些最常用的动词；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">转换角度，以物做主语，如go和spread两个词的例句；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">培养选择多样化的意识。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们这儿只是举了cold这一个例子，当然可以延伸出与更多的名词搭配，如cough, habit等，这些都会让学员进行反复练习，很快就会培养出学员自然而然地运用的意识。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例十一　各种off</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">训练内容：介词off与动词的搭配练习</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">动词与介词结合构成的短语对学员来说是比较难掌握的内容，也需要通过反复练习来掌握。off这个词就可以和很多的动词搭配表达丰富的含义。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 1</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与go, come, get, take等搭配表达很多意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 2</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与break, cut, turn, put, pull, push等搭配表达多个意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 3</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">与drive, laugh, see, sleep, walk, wash等搭配表达某个具体的意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上因为内容较多，不再一一给出例句，其中一些已经在前面的章节中讲过。学员通过练习会发现，off这个词实在太有用了，它与动词的搭配可以解决平时你解决不了的很多表达问题。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">主题训练</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这个练习主要是围绕着某一件事物进行的，目的是结合我们前面所学的内容，全方位训练学员对这个事物的描述能力。包括事物的结构、特性、发展变化，可以分名词、动词、形容词、介词等来描述。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例十二　京沪高速公路</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 1</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">用所学构成类和属性类名词描述“京沪高速公路”，如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">side（边）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It has two sides. Each side has two or three paths.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">part（部分）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The highway has different parts, for example, Beijing-jinan, Nanjing-shanghai.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">size（长度）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The whole distance of it is 1200 kilometers.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">position（位置）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">The starting point is at Beijing, the end is in Shanghai.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There're many tollgates along the road.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">There're many stations along the road. The drivers can have a break in these stations.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">quality（质量）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is a first-level highway.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 2</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">用所学形容词描述“京沪高速公路”，如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">长短</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is long.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">宽窄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is wide.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">直斜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is straight in most parts, but it is curved in some other parts.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">质地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is smooth in most parts, but it is rough in some other parts.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is strong.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It is firm enough for heavy traffic.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 3</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">用动词或动词短语来描述“京沪高速公路”，如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">本源词go, make</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It goes all the way from Beijing to Shanghai.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It was made in 1980s.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">位置类动词cover, connect, cross</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It covers Beijing, Shanghai and other four provinces.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It connects Beijing and Shanghai.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">It crosses with some other roads and railways along the way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">空间类动词close, clear</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">When the weather is bad, the road will be closed.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">When there is a car accident, the road needs to be cleared quickly for other vehicles to pass.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上只是举了部分例子，实际操作过程中学员还会碰撞出更多的火花来。如果把上面这些内容汇总起来的话，基本上就可以作为“百度百科”里面关于京沪高速的英文版本的介绍了。所以，这也作为一个活生生的例子证明了，虽然我们只学了1368个单词，但这些词的能量却是无限的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，这种系统的、分门别类的练习不仅仅适合用在road这种具体事物上，还可以用在人和其他事物上，就不再一一列举了。学员在做这些练习的时候一个最大的感受是：自己有话说了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">单词释义</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我们在上面提到的四大技能中最重要的一个是“自产自用”。这个技能是需要经过特别训练才能逐渐掌握的，就是我们现在所说的“单词释义”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">顾名思义，“单词释义”就是给单词下定义。这个训练有以下几个重要的作用：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">1.培养学员用大词的意识。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">单词释义大多是以名词的类别词或动词的上义词开头的，反复地练习可以让学员在最短时间内找到这些大词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">2.培养使用从句的意识。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">单词释义中经常会用到that, who, when, where打头的从句，而这些从句在口语中是经常会用到的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">3.提高“自产自用”说英语的技巧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">下面就以名词的释义和动词的释义为例进行说明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例十三　名词释义</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">训练内容：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请用R词汇表中的单词解释以下名词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
