            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">when</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">最后一个nail可以不用引导词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 3</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">找出释义从句中的关键词，有几个比较简单，另外几个对学员则有些难度，说明如下：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">helmet：关键词是keep</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">airport：关键是on, off</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">lift：关键词是take, up, down</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">nail：关键词是end</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">Step 4</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">补充其他成分，形成一个完整的单词释义，参考答案分别是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">colleague：A person who works with you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">cinema：A place where you go to see a film.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">helmet：A hat that keeps your head safe.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">airport：A place where people get on and off airplanes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">lift：A machine that takes people and things up and down in a high building.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">dawn：The time when the sun comes up.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">nail：The hard part at the end of a finger or toe.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这是词典中的标准答案，我们并不要求学员说得这么准确、简洁。只要他们的答案中有这些关键词就行了，语法上有些错误不用特别计较。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上还比较简单，像下面这两个就比较复杂了，真要达到这种程度，说明学员的英语思维能力和口语水平已经比较高了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">bicycle（自行车）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">A machine with two wheels that you can sit on and move yourlegs to make the wheel turn.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">anchor（锚）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">A heavy metal thing that you drop into the water from a boat to stop the boat from moving away.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例十四　动词释义</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">训练内容：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请用R词汇表中的单词解释以下动词：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">buy</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">hire</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">peel</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">imagine</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">scratch</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">hide</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">drink</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习的步骤与要求和前面的名词释义相似，就不再具体说明。请看参考答案：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">buy：Give money to get something.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">hire：Pay somebody to do work for you.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">peel：Take the skin off fruits or vegetables.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">imagine：Make a picture of something in your mind.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">scratch：Move your fingers across your skin.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">hide：Put something where people can not see.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">drink：Take in liquid, for example water, milk or coffee, through your mouth.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">需要说明的是，以上释义都是在口语中可以直接运用的，用来丰富自己的表达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h3 class=\"bodycontent-third-title\">语序训练</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我在《英语思维是这样炼成的》一书中曾提到过中英文表达语序的不同，通常情况下，英语是先说主语和谓语，然后把其他成分放在后面，而汉语则经常是把其他成分夹在主语和谓语中间。这种差别会造成学员在表达时的混乱，所以也需要通过专门的训练解决这种思维上的差异。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">事实上，除了单个句子上有这种差别外，两种语言在段落上也存在着这种差别。英语倾向于把核心观点或者结论放在一段话的开头，而把解释性的、描述性的句子放在其后。所以，我们就创造了另外一种有特色的语序训练方式：翻译新闻标题。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">新闻标题是一种高度浓缩的文体，短短一句话包含着丰富的信息量，所以，用它来做训练题材很有效。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h4 class=\"sigil_not_in_toc\">案例十五　翻译新闻标题</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">训练内容：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">请用英语讲述下面一段新闻标题的内容：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">患癌女孩被父母、男友遗弃后去世</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">练习说明：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这段文字在前面的章节中曾经用过。这个标题虽然只有短短十四个字，但却说了三件事：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">1.一个女孩得了癌症；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">2.她死了；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">3.死前，父母和男友抛弃了她。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">一开始学员总是试图用一句话把这个事说完，我总要再三提醒他们，现在这个阶段不要急着一口吃个胖子，你们还没达到CCTV国际频道编辑的程度，还是老老实实先做些力所能及的事情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以，我们对学员的要求是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">1.一句话说一件事情，哪怕只有主语和谓语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">2.先把整个事件中最重要的事情说出来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以，我们希望学员做到的差不多就是下面这个样子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">A girl died. She got a cancer.Her parents and her boyfriend left her before she died.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">就是前面所说的那三句话，只不过顺序上有了侧重。这段表达虽然简单，但却清晰、准确，没有任何一个老外会误解你所播报的这段新闻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">以上列举的各种训练方式仅仅是我们教学实践中的一部分，我们还在不断开发新的输入输出模式，但无论是哪一种，都是本着体验性的原则。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">等条件具备的时候，我们很可能会成立一个专业的摄制组，录制属于自己的教学视频。这些教学视频与大家平常看的美剧或其他原汁原味的教学视频会有一个明显的区别，那就是，所有的录制现场都是咱们中国人最熟悉的生活或工作场景，可能是在菜市场，也可能是在大排档，可能是在公司年会，也可能是在高考考场。总之，我们就是要把英语渗透到你的学习、生活、工作中去，让你学得快、用得上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\">\n  </div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><h1 class=\"bodycontent-first-title\">后记</h1></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">在键盘上敲下正文的最后一个字，我如释重负。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">自2010年我的第一本书《英语思维是这样炼成的》出版之后一直到现在，我只做了一件事，就是成立了一个小型的培训机构，亲自授课，把我在书中关于英语思维的理论付诸实践。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">我深知前一本书所写的更多的只是理论，要想把它转化为一套真正有效的学习模式，必须经过实践的检验并不断完善。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">所以，虽然《英语思维是这样炼成的》自出版到现在已获得了10万册不菲的销量，并被评为“2012—2013年度行业优秀畅销书”，也曾荣幸地被一些高校英语专业的老师选为学生的课外参考书，并且出版社两年前就不断地催促我再版，同时还不断地有投资人希望我能够扩大学校的规模，但我还是决定沉下心来，排除一切干扰与诱惑，聚精会神地在可控范围内进行我的英语思维训练。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">因为我知道我可以做得更好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">四年的实践结果也证明了我可以做得更好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">四年的时间里，我先后招收了三百多个学员。在这三百多个学员中，约有一半的学员目前在外企的工作环境中使用英语。换句话说，我的学员中有50%左右通过我的英语培训机构提高了英语水平，并利用自己的英语技能找到了一份理想的工作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">这已经是一个让我满意的结果了。因为教过英语的人都知道，一个人能否学好英语是多方面因素决定的，除了教学方法与老师的教学水平外，个人接受能力、努力程度等都起着重要的作用。我不敢说我培训过的学员每个人都能够说一口流利的英语，但我敢说，无论是直接参加我的英语授课的人，或者是仅仅参加我们网络课程的人，只要能坚持在规定时间内把所有的课程上完，并完成所有的课外作业，就一定可以说一口流利的英语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">甚至只要是您看完这本书，哪怕不参加我们的英语培训，只是按照书里的内容和学习方法进行学习，您的英语也能获得质的飞跃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1f83596b9618251c/text/000003658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1f83596b9618251c-a62746 twpub-1f83596b9618251c-9882b5\"><p class=\"bodycontent-text\">最后，感谢大家的支持，也衷心地希望得到大家的意见和反馈。</p></div>"
        },
